  <para style="mt1">MARKUS</para>
  <para style="im">Nabari Manayi shi Markus ɓei ka</para>
  <para style="im">Nyakayi–Markus nu</para>
  <para style="im">Aba nwo ɓei dna–Roma</para>
  <para style="im">Aye–A.D. 60–65</para>
  <para style="im">Aɓo nɓa kafi–Yohanna Markus ɓei zhin wo gnisun n Bulus yi. Wa lo wa dna n Roma aba wo ɓei ka anya nwo ɓei wo n Bitrus.</para>
  <para style="im">Markus aɓeda wo ngye oza nu nwo zhin awye seida da, nya kwo ɓei zhin wa ka nyi, wo ɓei ye wa ye nabari manayi ye zhi nna ba gmanyi nu. Woi wu shi Yesu ɓei zhin tnu-tnu, wa kmazo n Yesu amyipyeyi kmaknayi nnanyi. Wa ya ngye shi Yesu ɓei ya wo tnu-tnu, n wazi Shekwoyi ebe mi nya yi. Wa da wo fiɓodna asura (8:31; 9:31; 10:33 ) a zun wodu wa fi ntu anyi alaifi ɓo.</para>
  <para style="iot">Aɓo-tukwo:</para>
  <para style="io1">1 Yohanna batizma–zhin yi n Yesu batizmayi <char style="ior"><ref loc="MRK 1:1-13">1:1-13</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">2. Yesu tnu-tnu n Galili <char style="ior"><ref loc="MRK 1:14-9:50">1:14–9:50</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">3. Wa lo Urushelima <char style="ior"><ref loc="MRK 10:1-11:26">10:1–11:26</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">4. Agna-na kni kpe aje <char style="ior"><ref loc="MRK 11:27-12:44">11:27–12:44</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">5. Ɓeda tu aɓo nɓa ɓe lo nabye <char style="ior"><ref loc="MRK 13:1-37">13:1-37</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">6. Yesu fi nwo kala-lai nvingwo <char style="ior"><ref loc="MRK 14:1-16:20">14:1–16:20</ref></char></para>
  <para style="imte1">Markus</para>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="MRK 1"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 1:1"/>Nabari manayi Yesu Kristi Shekwoyi Nugun nya kwo ya nlayi nu.<verse eid="MRK 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 1:2"/>Ngye shi a cei kafi dna Anabi Ishaya Litafi, Shekwoyi ɓei da ge, Wo ɓa tnu Wo ɓi yi dna nanyi, ama owo tnu-tnu dai ɓa ɓe na bye wa zhin anyi zhi ntu wo ɓe-ɓe ɓo. <verse eid="MRK 1:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 1:3"/>“Tnu-tnu dai ye ɓei dna zhabui nu, wa da nabari ge aza vinya ɓa zhin ɓa sese aba kafin Dagayi wo ɓe,” nya nu Ishaya ɓei da.<verse eid="MRK 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Yohanna Batizma Zhinyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 1:4"/>Tnu-tnu dai ye nu ɓo zhin Yohanna Baptisma zhin-yi. Wo ɓo dna zhabui nu woi wu ge, aza vinya ɓapmi avun wu laifi, n na ɓai Shekwoyi wa zhin ɓa gafara, a zhin ɓa baptisma, kwa wu ge lallei ɓa la vun pmi wu laifi. <verse eid="MRK 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 1:5"/>Azayi knu n Urushelima n Yahudiya yi, ɓai zanzan fi Yahudiya bmana ɓa gye, ɓai wo Yohanna. Sa n ɓa ɓei yabui, wa zhin ɓa baptisma dna Urdin ʼla. <verse eid="MRK 1:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 1:6"/>Laknumi pa nu ɓei zhin wo je o wo shinpanya epanya nu. Aɓo, n ʼsu zhabui nyai nu ɓei zhin wo nyagyi. <verse eid="MRK 1:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 1:7"/>Wo ɓei zhin wo zhin waʼazi lai nu!</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 1:7">“Zaho ɓe lo safyewyi nwo du mi lo, har mi to knuce lo ma zhin wo baram. <verse eid="MRK 1:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 1:8"/>Mi zhin fye baptisma n nuwan yi, ama wo ɓei zhin fye baptisma n Shekwoyi Zafun yi.”<verse eid="MRK 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 1:9"/>Nwyi-hoi Yesu wa gmi n Nazarat n Galili. Yohanna wa zhin Wo baptisma n Urdun ʼla. <verse eid="MRK 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 1:10"/>Sa Yesu ɓei gmi ɓe n nuwan, wa gye eshe a guya, Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi n gye lukpe kwoi yatu Wo. <verse eid="MRK 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 1:11"/>Begye kwa gmi she, kwa cige, “Oho nu zhin Mi Nugun yeyeyi, Oho nu zhin Ma Gmada.”<verse eid="MRK 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 1:12"/>Nsayi-sayi yi, Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa lo woi n bmana. <verse eid="MRK 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 1:13"/>N zhabui mi Owa nyipyei shinyi n wo gmanyi yi akpe a nyafanya. Shaitan woi zhin Wo jaraba, N na vun amalayika ɓe ɓa zhin Wa tna.<verse eid="MRK 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 1:14"/>Nsa dohoyi, Esu Hiridus, woi la Yohanna wan, Yesu wa lo Galili, waʼazi zhin Shekwoyi nabari manayi nya.<verse eid="MRK 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 1:15"/>Wa ci ge, “Esa lasi n sayi, Shekwoyi bemi la wo vivi, fye pmi avun wu fya laifi, fya gwo Wo nabari manayi ye.”<verse eid="MRK 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Wa Yi Aɓnu-Tnuyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 1:16"/>Nwyi-hoi, sa Yesu ɓei zan-zan lo n Galili ʼla gbe, Wa gye Siman n wo zadoyi, Andarawus, ɓai wan awyesala ntuge oɓa bwaze nu ɓei nu.<verse eid="MRK 1:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 1:17"/>Yesu wa yi ɓa, “Fye ɓe fya vi Mi Miɓa zefye a zawan-yi.” <verse eid="MRK 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 1:18"/>Nsayi-sayi yi, ɓa fwa ɓa ʼsa, ɓa lo ngnisun woi.<verse eid="MRK 1:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 1:19"/>Nɓa bye fyewyi, Wa gye Zabadi aɓi, Yakubu n Yohanna yi, ɓai zhinɓa asa aba. <verse eid="MRK 1:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 1:20"/>Wa yi ɓa ce, Nsayi-sayi yi, ɓa fwa ɓa dada Zabadi, dna n ʼya, n na kodogoda yi n wo ɓei yi ɓa ɓa viwo nyi.<verse eid="MRK 1:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 1:21"/>Yesu n Wa nugundoyi, ɓa ɓe Kafarnafum Nsatiwyi, nlabmiyi ɓa lo a Yahudawayi aduwa nyakun Wa zhin waʼazi. <verse eid="MRK 1:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 1:22"/>Ca wo aza mwa, ntu ge Wo ɓei daɓo n ikoi gbo n na zaje nya yi. N tu ge Wo to ɓei shan azam.<verse eid="MRK 1:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aza Cbo-gbo Ba Bwa Kagna</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 1:23"/>Ezaho n alijenu ɓei dna n aduwa nyakun wa ya wyiɓe. <verse eid="MRK 1:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 1:24"/>“Knihin nu zhin Hoi gna yi gnagna ya, Yesu Nazaratiyi, Ha ɓe Ha wuyi nu? Mi kpe Ho ye lo, Shekwoyi Nugun Gyi-gyi-yi.” <verse eid="MRK 1:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 1:25"/>Yesu wa gna alijanu yi ge, wola ce pi wa pmi wa gmiya ɓe n zahi mi. <verse eid="MRK 1:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 1:26"/>Zafun nukwoyi ho, wa sa wyi wa pmi wa she zahi ya, wa gmiya ɓe n sayi. <verse eid="MRK 1:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 1:27"/>Ca wo aza mwa, ɓa daɓo ɓai cige, “Kni adini woi-woyi nu nyia? Har a zafun nukwoyi wo Wo begye.”<verse eid="MRK 1:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 1:28"/>Nabari deye kwa gnami, har Galili kni vinya.<verse eid="MRK 1:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29-30" style="v" pubnumber="29,30" sid="MRK 1:29-30"/> Sa n ɓa ɓei fwa aduwa nyakun, Owo, n wa barayi ɓa lo Siman n Andarawus yi puva. Ɓa gye Siman yezhi dna n nayi-napye kaladayi, ɓa gna Yesu wo ɓo n sayi-sayi yi. <verse eid="MRK 1:29-30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 1:31"/>Walo wo gado gbe, Wa shiwo bwa Wa bmawo zhin wa sase, nayi-napye yi ho kwa fawo, wa laka n sayi wa zhin ɓa nyagyi.<verse eid="MRK 1:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32-33" style="v" pubnumber="32,33" sid="MRK 1:32-33"/> N wyeshe yi a kpemi ɓa nu, na nyasan yi n na lijanu dayi, n na bai Wa ka ba gna. Aza n mwa begye ɓa kun n Kafarnafum zhimi n na bayi ɓa gye Wo. <verse eid="MRK 1:32-33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 1:34"/>Yesu wa ka aza gna n wyeshe-yi n mwa. Wa gnakni alijanu ge ɓa kun na za mi. (Amma woto ɓei ye ge alijanu da ɓom, ntu ge ɓa kpewo-ye lo.)<verse eid="MRK 1:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 1:35"/>N labmi yi Wa kpesa, Wa laka Wa lo zhabui, Wa zhin aduwa.<verse eid="MRK 1:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36-37" style="v" pubnumber="36,37" sid="MRK 1:36-37"/> Nsa dohoi Siman n na zajeyi ɓa lo Wo zanyi, ɓa gna Wo ge, “A za nya Ho ɓo lo.”<verse eid="MRK 1:36-37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 1:38"/>Ama Wa dna ɓegbe ge, “Dole ya lo a zhido, Mi gna ɓa nabari ce, gama Maɓe ntu cenu.”<verse eid="MRK 1:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 1:39"/>Wa zan laɓa n Galili kni, woi zhin waʼazi n na aduwa nyakun, woi lo a zaya mwa na lijenu iko. <verse eid="MRK 1:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 1:40"/>Nsa hoi Kuturu wa ɓe wa yashi n Wa bye wa gyi Wo wye ge, Wo kawo gna. “Nhaye, Ho bami Ha kami gna.” Bma mi Zhin.<verse eid="MRK 1:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 1:41"/>Yesu wa gye wo sun-sun Wa towo bwa Wa cige, “Mi laye, la kagna!” <verse eid="MRK 1:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 1:42"/>Nsayi-sayi yi, wa kagna bwa.<verse eid="MRK 1:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43-44" style="v" pubnumber="43,44" sid="MRK 1:43-44"/> Yesu wa gnawo, “Lo Ayahudawayi pirist aba wo dnahowye. To kpe gni ha da ɓo n zayi n zokwom, lo n nyaga yi shi n Musa ɓei zun tu kuturu n wo la kagna bwa n nabayi a za kpe lallei hola lafiya bwa.”<verse eid="MRK 1:43-44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 1:45"/>Ama sa n wo ɓei lo n zokwo, wa ya wyidna ge wola lafiya bwa, n tu cenu aza shekna Yesu har to wami nwo lo ezhi doho-doho yim, sai dna zhabui mi azayi knu na bai gbo-gbo ɓai ɓe dawo ɓo.<verse eid="MRK 1:45"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="MRK 2"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 2:1"/>Anyipyei mwa begye navun, wa, jezeɓe Kapanahum, nabari Owo ɓe-ɓenya kwa gnami n zhi wolo-wolo. <verse eid="MRK 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 2:2"/>Puwa n wo ɓei dnanyi, nu n na zayi har to ai bwa aba na boknumi gbem. Wa zhin ɓa waʼazi. <verse eid="MRK 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 2:3"/>Aza n gun anyi ɓa ɓe n zayi shi n nayi-fi-fiyi-ya n nyasan yi. <verse eid="MRK 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 2:4"/>To ɓa bwa aba n ɓasi Yesu a bam, ɓa bma nyakunshe ɓa shin nyasan-yi shi n Yesu abye.<verse eid="MRK 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 2:5"/>Sa n Yesu ɓei gye ɓa gaiciyaga, Wa ci nyasan-yi ge, “Aku ha laifi zhin gafara.”<verse eid="MRK 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6-7" style="v" pubnumber="6,7" sid="MRK 2:6-7"/> Ama A Yahudawayi adini tukwoda ɓa dafi a ɓa mi, “Deye kwonu zhin (tukwo-mwa). Wo zhin nubo ge Wo zhin Shekwoyi nu? Gama Shekwoyi gmanyi Wonu zhin gafara zhinyi.”<verse eid="MRK 2:6-7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8-9" style="v" pubnumber="8,9" sid="MRK 2:8-9"/> Yesu ɓei kpe ɓa bugba ye, Wa ci ɓa ge, “Knihi nu zhin cei wo fya? Kni dei nu dulo n fwa-fwa a ci ge a ku gafara zhin wo, ko a la wo kagna? <verse eid="MRK 2:8-9"/><verse number="10-11" style="v" pubnumber="10,11" sid="MRK 2:10-11"/> Ma wu fye ge Emi; ʼZa Nugun n ikoyi lo Ma zhin wo gafara, Wa pmi wye da nyasan-yi Wa ciwo ge, a la ho kagna. Ku ha pece ha lo ho puwa!”<verse eid="MRK 2:10-11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 2:12"/>Wa gya gna gun she wa ku wo pece wa gmiya lo bmi. Ca wo aza mwa ɓai la Shekwoyi tu, “Yi to shin degye pya gyem.”<verse eid="MRK 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 2:13"/>Yesu wa je gmi ya lo Ola gbe, Wa zhan za waʼazi nɓa ɓei shekna Wo nyi. <verse eid="MRK 2:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 2:14"/>She wo ɓei zan-zan Woi v i la gbe, Wa gye Levi Alfas nugun n sase tu nwo agadu gwo ba. Yesu wa ciwo ge, “Knuɓe Miyi, ɓe ha ze Mi bara.” Levi wa laka sa wa kun lo woi!<verse eid="MRK 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 2:15"/>Nsukwoyi Levi wa yi wo agadu gwoyi aje n na laifida a dnagmai yi n na nyagyi gyi ba, n na bayi ɓa sun n Yesu yi, n Wo abarayi. (A laifida ye pya ɓei mwa begye n na za nɓa ɓei viwo nyi.) <verse eid="MRK 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 2:16"/>Ama sa na Yahudawayi adini tukwoda ɓei gye Yesu woi gyi nyagyi n na laifi dayi, ɓa ci Wo abara ge, “Knihi nu zhin Woi mi Woi gyi nyagyi n na laifida yia?”<verse eid="MRK 2:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 2:17"/>Sa n Yesu ɓei wo ɓa ɓeda Wa ciɓa ge, “Anyasan-yi nu n shigbeda apma yi, toge alafiya dam. Mi to ɓe Ma gna a za manayi nu ge ɓa ye abui m, sai aza nukoyi.”<verse eid="MRK 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Oza Nwa Gmi Nshe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 2:18"/>Saho lo n Yohanna a bara n na Yahudawayi atukwodayi ɓei zhin azumi. Wato to ɓai gyi nyagyim, shi ɓa adini ɓei wu ɓa. Nwyihoi ɓa ɓe Yesu aba ɓa nyawo, ɓo kwo zhin to Wo abara yi zhin azumin.<verse eid="MRK 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 2:19"/>Yesu wa dnaɓa ɓegbe ge, “Mulaɓa anugundo zhin ɓa na nyagyi n muia ɓa zhin? Ɓa ɓa wun bugba woye kunsun n ɓai?” <verse eid="MRK 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 2:20"/>Ama n wyihoi a ɓei laɓa mulaɓa nsayi nu nɓa ɓei wun bugba. <verse eid="MRK 2:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 2:21"/>(Azumi shi zhin zokwo kwo-kwoyi fye nu) Kwo ze ngye a gu eje kwo-kwoyi ta n je woi-woyi nu. She paci yi ɓei je saya ma? Obwo woyi kwa du kwokwoyi pata. <verse eid="MRK 2:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 2:22"/>Fye gna ce yekpe lo, nge n na fi anab nuwan woi-woyi n Pwakun kwo-kwoyi, sa anab nuwan ɓei to gunzhi, pwakun ɓei ɓaya anab nuwan a zhangma. Anab nuwan woyi ye pwakun woyi nu.<verse eid="MRK 2:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 2:23"/>Nwyihoi njesun, n Satiwyiyi, Yesu n Wo abara yi ɓai zan-zan fi nfwa, O Wo abara ɓa bma alkama tukwo ɓai gyi.<verse eid="MRK 2:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 2:24"/>Sa na Yahudawayi adini tukwoda ɓei gye lonu, ɓa ci Yesu ge, “Oho abara zun wyidna gna nu, a ta do alkama n Satiwyiyin.”<verse eid="MRK 2:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25-26" style="v" pubnumber="25,26" sid="MRK 2:25-26"/> Ama Yesu wa ciɓa ge, “Fye to shin wo esa mikun ɓei gun Esu Dawuda nwa nugun-doyi, wa lo Shekwoyi puwa–Abiyata nu ɓei zhin pirist yakwo n sayi–ɓa gyi bredi n na pirist nu ɓei zhin ɓai bwakwo gyim. Degye ɓei zhin laifi nu nkwohin. <verse eid="MRK 2:25-26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 2:27"/>Ama a ɓei zhin Satiwyi ntu za ampanyi ɓo nu toge! Satiwyi na gyi gyiba n zayim. <verse eid="MRK 2:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 2:28"/>Emi, Eza Nugun, n ikoyi lo Ma da nya na za ɓa mi ɓa zhin n Satiwyi yi!”<verse eid="MRK 2:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="MRK 3"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 3:1"/>Sa Yesu ɓei dna n Kafarnafum Wa lo aduwa nyakun njesun Wa gye za dna nbwai sha-shayi. <verse eid="MRK 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 3:2"/>Shikwonyi Satiwyi nu ɓei, Yesu a nuwun-yi ɓai ka wo wye ko Wo ɓa ka zayi bwa gna. N Wa kawo gna, ɓa ɓei shiri zhin ɓa wan wo.<verse eid="MRK 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 3:3"/>Yesu wa yi zayi ɓe ceyi gni na za bye. <verse eid="MRK 3:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 3:4"/>Wa pmi awye shi owo anuwun yi Wa nya ge, “Ko bimya a zhin ɓo manayi n Satiwyiyi? Kwo nyipyei ɓenukwoi zhin nya na? Kwo zhin nyipyei a-wye-wyei gni nya nu kwo oɓa wu nya na?” Amma to ɓa dna Wo ɓe gbe m. <verse eid="MRK 3:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 3:5"/>Wa shiɓa wye n mina-gyi yi, ntu ge ce ɓei san Wo shi ɓata gye ɓa anuwan n nyai n aza yem. Wa ci zayi ho ge, “Ta ho bwaya,” Sa n wo ɓo takwoya, wa bwa kagna n sayi-sayi yi.<verse eid="MRK 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 3:6"/>Nsayi-sayi yi a Farisiyi ɓa lo Hirudus azaba ɓa zhin shaula shi ɓa ɓa wu Yesu. <verse eid="MRK 3:6"/><verse number="7-8" style="v" pubnumber="7,8" sid="MRK 3:7-8"/> Nsa deye, Yesu nwo abara yi, ɓa lo olagbe deji yi viɓa nɓa ɓo knu n Galili kni, n Yahudiya yi, n Urushelima yi, n Udumiyayi, wato Urdun la kma har kwoi lo Taya n Sida kni yi. Ntuge owa ɓo wowoyi zhin nabari ɓo la gnami n kpai, ntu cenu azai ɓe wo gye n ɓahin tukwoyi.<verse eid="MRK 3:7-8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 3:9"/>Wa gna Wo abara ge, ɓa ɓe eya yi vivi yi, sakun a ce Wa bwaya dna nuwan, ntuge deji ɓo ku duwyi. <verse eid="MRK 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 3:10"/>Ntuge Wo ɓola aza kagna n wyi yi mwa, ntu lo nu anyasanyi mwa ɓa she kna Wo, ɓai ye ɓa to Wo bwa.<verse eid="MRK 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 3:11"/>Sanu alijanu da gye Wo wye, ɓa miya zhi kni, ɓai fyaku, “Oho nu zhin Shekwoyi Nugun!” <verse eid="MRK 3:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 3:12"/>Ama Wa gna kni ɓa ge, ɓa to zhin a kpe Wo yem.<verse eid="MRK 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aje Atnu-tnuyi Ho Yi Ɓe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 3:13"/>Nnavun deye, Wa gnu lo pe, Wa gna Wa za kni-kni yi ho ge ɓa ɓe ɓa sun Woi ɓo, ɓa ku zhin lonu. <verse eid="MRK 3:13"/><verse number="14-15" style="v" pubnumber="14,15" sid="MRK 3:14-15"/> Nsayi Wa kni aza n ɓami n gun awo-cei-aba ɓa ze Wa nugundo, Wa tnu ɓa, ɓa zhin waʼazi, ɓai knu alijanu ya.<verse eid="MRK 3:14-15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16-19" style="v" sid="MRK 3:16-19"/>Aza ʼye awo-cei-aba nyi, n Wo ɓo kninyi: Siman (Wa shan wo ye tu ge Bitrus), Yakubu n Yohanna yi (Zabadi a ɓi ama Yesu ɓei yi ɓa ge, Ogmawyisa aɓi), Andarawus, Filibus, Batalamawus, Matta, Toma, Yakubu (Alfas nugun), Tadawus, Siman (wo ɓei dna naza nɓa sun kun ɓa mi a Romawayi gwamnati ya nyi.) Yahuda Iskariyoti (nwo ɓo knu Yesu nyi.)<verse eid="MRK 3:16-19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 3:20"/>Sa nwo ɓo jeze ɓe puwa nwo ɓei dna nyi, aza ya yezhi njesun, har to Wa bwa sa n Wo gyi nyagyi m. <verse eid="MRK 3:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 3:21"/>Sa n Wo anugun-do ɓei wo lonu, ɓa zhin atna ɓa lo Woi n ɓa puwa. Ɓa cige, “Wo ta kpeɓeye lo n Wo zhin m!”<verse eid="MRK 3:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Laifi Nkwo To N Gafara Yim</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 3:22"/>Amma a Yahudawayi a malami n ɓa ɓo knu Urushelima, ɓa cige, “shetan, alijanu-su dna lo n wo mi. Cenu zhin alijanu yi wo-wo ɓeda.”<verse eid="MRK 3:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 3:23"/>Yesu wa yi ɓa zhi Wa nya ɓa ɓo “woi si anyi besis nɓa ɓo kpeye Shetan ɓa zhin wuna wa nya shetan ya? <verse eid="MRK 3:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 3:24"/>Ebe n kwo gna je nkwohin tukwo yi, kwo ɓa miya. <verse eid="MRK 3:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 3:25"/>Puwa n kwo na je gna yi, kwota gni m. <verse eid="MRK 3:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 3:26"/>N shetan sungun n wohin yi, woɓa mi n ɓoho zhin wuna. Wo ta pwo m! <verse eid="MRK 3:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 3:27"/>(Sai a pa shetan, kafin a knu alijanu ya), ngye sai a pa zakala kpa, kafin ami a lo wo puwa a wyi wo akaya.<verse eid="MRK 3:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 3:28"/>“Eminu gna fye, aɓa zhin laifi doho-dohoi gafara, kwo eza woi yi Mi n ye nukwoyi yi. <verse eid="MRK 3:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 3:29"/>Ama ɓeda nukwoyi tu n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi tukwo, ata zin za gafara m, laifi yakwonu.”<verse eid="MRK 3:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 3:30"/>Wo ɓo gna ɓa lo nu n tu ge, ɓa ɓo cige Wo zhin Wa tnu-tnu a wowoyi n shetan ikoyi nu. (Maimako ɓa cige n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi iko yinu.)<verse eid="MRK 3:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31-32" style="v" pubnumber="31,32" sid="MRK 3:31-32"/> Owo ʼya n Wa majeyi, ɓa ɓe puwa n naza ɓo yefi woi wuɓa nya nyi, ɓa tnu wo yi ɓa daɓo n Woi “Oho ʼya n Ha majeyi, n Ho ɓei pmalo n bmi ɓa daɓo hoi.”<verse eid="MRK 3:31-32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 3:33"/>“Wa dnaɓo gbe ge, Anyikanu zhin Mi ya? Nyikanu zhin Ma majeʼa?” <verse eid="MRK 3:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 3:34"/>Wa shi aza ʼwye n ba ɓei shewo kna nyi Wa ci ge, “Emi ʼya, n Ma majeyi nu zhi nyi! <verse eid="MRK 3:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 3:35"/>Eza n wo zhin Shekwoyi ɓeye, wo nu zhin Mi Mado, emi mapui, n Mi ʼya yi!”<verse eid="MRK 3:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="MRK 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Wa Wu Aza Nya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 4:1"/>Nsa dohoi njesun, aza yezhi n Wo aba n ʼlagbe woi wu ɓa nya. Walo Wa sase dna n ʼya Wa daɓo ɓai dna ɓo. <verse eid="MRK 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 4:2"/>Wo ɓei zhin Wa wunya Woi si aza anyi ɓesi nu ndu. Wa si ba doho layi:<verse eid="MRK 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 4:3"/>“Fye wo! Fwa-yi ho ɓei lo anya bye. Shi wo ɓei she nya-bye n wo fwa, <verse eid="MRK 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 4:4"/>Adoho ɓa kaya zhi zokwo, alu ɓaɓe ɓa tnuɓa ɓa gyi. <verse eid="MRK 4:4"/><verse number="5-6" style="v" pubnumber="5,6" sid="MRK 4:5-6"/> Adoho ɓa kaya kpe na gbaku-ku, ba pye pai, ama safyewi nyipyeyi kwa woɓa ɓa ku fyi, ntu ge oɓa gbegye to lo kni lo m. <verse eid="MRK 4:5-6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 4:7"/>Adoho ɓa kaya fyi n Knawuyi, aknawuyi ɓa kuɓa gyi sun to ba fya wye m. <verse eid="MRK 4:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 4:8"/>Ama adoho ɓa kaya fyi n kni manayi, ba ga ampani aku shita n du ʼdo nwo ɓo bye nyi, adoho aku shi-tnanyi, adoho har aku tagyi. <verse eid="MRK 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 4:9"/>Nfye na tnubua yi gyilo, fya wo!”<verse eid="MRK 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 4:10"/>Nnavun sa n ɓa ɓei cezhi n Wo abara awo-cei-aba yi, n Wo aviyi hoi jesun, ɓa nya Wo “Yiye Ha wuyi oho anyi-ɓesi-si awyega.”<verse eid="MRK 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11-12" style="v" pubnumber="11,12" sid="MRK 4:11-12"/> Wa ciɓa ge, “Ala ga fye fya kpe aɓoho ye tu n Shekwoyi bemi tukwo, n ɓa zhin asiri nu nna za ba nɓa ta kpe Wo yem. She anabi Ishaya cei da, ‘Ko da shike ɓa gyelo, ɓai wo, ɓata kpe awye ga m, n na bai ɓa pmida Shekwoyi, Wa zhin ɓa gafara m.’ ” <verse eid="MRK 4:11-12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 4:13"/>“Ama n fye to kep anyi ɓesisi ɓiyi ye awyega m, fye ɓa kpe ajeye wuna n Miye Ma da nyia? <verse eid="MRK 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 4:14"/>Fwayi n Ma dawo ɓo nyi, ezanu n wo lo n Shekwoyi ɓedayi, woi zhin kukari wa bye kwo n za bugba.<verse eid="MRK 4:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 4:15"/>“Zokwo n nyabye ho ɓei kaya zhi nyi, kwo wu gye a-za n ɓa na kuta ɓugbayi fyi. Sa n ɓa wo Shekwoyi ɓeda, Shetan wa ɓe n sayi-sayi yi, wa zhin ɓa ɓa zo kwa mwi. <verse eid="MRK 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 4:16"/>Agbakuku kni nya wu gye a-za n ɓa wo Shekwoyi ɓeda na gmadayi, <verse eid="MRK 4:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 4:17"/>ama ngye agebegbe putu nu fyi n kni-yi pya, oɓa gbegye to lo shin n kpayin, koda shike ɓa zhin ɓa bmiya kmisun yi, sa n wahala bwa ɓa, ɓa fyi.<verse eid="MRK 4:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 4:18"/>“Ekni akna-wuyi nya wugye aza n ɓa wo Shekwoyi ɓeda ɓa gwo kwo. <verse eid="MRK 4:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 4:19"/>Ama safyewyi aɓowye-da anyinya, n nyabwa ye yi, n na bye-gyi zanyi yi, n na nya manayi shakpe yi, ɓa ɓe ɓa ku Shekwoyi ɓeda gyi sun n ɓa bugba, har to ɓa zhin ampanyi m.<verse eid="MRK 4:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 4:20"/>“Ama ekni manayi nya, wugye aza bugbanu n ɓa wo Shekwoyi ɓeda ɓa gwo kwo n shince kniyi, ɓa ga ampanyi shita, shitnai, har tagyi, ndu odo n na ɓo bye nɓa bugba nyi.” <verse eid="MRK 4:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 4:21"/>Wa nyaɓa ge, “Sa n za dna fitila na, wo zhin wa ɓe n bue yi wa knu kwo?” Awo! Ata gye buzangna har a zhin ampanyi n ceyi m, A zhin a ya fitila tu n nya nu nkwo ɓa ga buzangna dai-dai a bwa kwo gyiba.<verse eid="MRK 4:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 4:22"/>Oɓo kwo bwishi lo nsayi ye, aɓa kpekwa nyaya n wyihoi. <verse eid="MRK 4:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 4:23"/>Nfye na tnubuayi gyilo, fyewo! <verse eid="MRK 4:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 4:24"/>Fye zhin ɓo fya wo, N fya zhin lonu, fye ɓa gna awyega bwa nɓo Mi gna fye nyi. <verse eid="MRK 4:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 4:25"/>Eza n wo nya yi lo aɓa gawo, eza n wo to cei lon, odo n wo cei lo ma aɓa kwo gwo wo.<verse eid="MRK 4:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 4:26"/>Fye wo anyi ɓe sisi deye, Fya kpe shi Shekwoyi ebemi wu. <verse eid="MRK 4:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 4:27"/>Fwayi ho ɓo bye anya nwo fwa, wa lo wo nya: anya pa har ba mwa n tnawo bamzhin. <verse eid="MRK 4:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 4:28"/>Ntuge ekni nu ɓo zhin nyabye kwa mwa. Kmisun-yi, fyintolo nu ɓo gmi be kpa, n sayi alkama tukwo ɓa ɓe har ɓa ɓi. <verse eid="MRK 4:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 4:29"/>Kwonu o fwada ɓe sagmanyi yi nwo limzhegye yi wa gbe ɓa.<verse eid="MRK 4:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 4:30"/>Yesu wa nyage, “Mi ba wufye shi Shekwoyi bemi wun n wunana? Miba gbekwodo n knihin nu fya bwa awyega?” <verse eid="MRK 4:30"/><verse number="31-32" style="v" pubnumber="31,32" sid="MRK 4:31-32"/> Kwo wu gye mustard byegye nu. Kwo bwa sun ciwyi nu, ama shi kwo mwa, kwo zhin kwa du a shinwa ʼje mwa-mwa n na bwalayi mwakpa har aluyi ɓe ɓai kpa ma n kwa bwala.<verse eid="MRK 4:31-32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 4:33"/>Wa si ɓa anyi ɓesi n mwa shi ɓa ɓa mi ɓa bwa awyega. <verse eid="MRK 4:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 4:34"/>Behin-hin, wo ɓei zhin Woi wu nya, n nanyi ɓe-sisi yi nu du n deji aba, ama sa n Wa pmigni n Wa barayi, Wa wuɓa awyega. <verse eid="MRK 4:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 4:35"/>Sa wyeshe ɓei she, Yesu wa gna Wo abara ge, “Yi piya lo nuwan kma deyi.” <verse eid="MRK 4:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 4:36"/>Ɓa lo ɓa ya aza zhi (kwo da yake aya je ɓei vi ɓa na vun). <verse eid="MRK 4:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 4:37"/>Safyewyi agmasa ci, anuwan dokwo ɓa kuka ɓai ce eya abwa ya, nuwan ye kwa nu eya-har kwoi ye kwa shin. <verse eid="MRK 4:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 4:38"/>Yesu ɓei la wangye dna eya avun tu na gyewan nya. Ɓa knu Wo agyewyi ya ɓai gna, “Male, Ho tagye Ha nuwan lo n yi bwi-bwi ɓo yin?”<verse eid="MRK 4:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 4:39"/>Wa gnakni se, Wa ci ola ge, “La ce pyi” Ese, n na nuwan dokwoyi, ɓa ze cei pyi.<verse eid="MRK 4:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 4:40"/>Wa nya ɓa ge, “Knihin nu ɓo zhin fyei wodna? Har saiye fye to gami Gaiciya n?”<verse eid="MRK 4:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 4:41"/>Ca wo ɓa ɓai gna je ge, “Nyikado pya nu dna n zaye ya, har ese n ʼlayi ɓai wo-wo ɓeda?”<verse eid="MRK 4:41"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="MRK 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Abulutu Ɓa Fi Oza Ce N Wye-Wye Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1-2" style="v" pubnumber="1,2" sid="MRK 5:1-2"/> Shi ɓa ɓei piya kpe nkma dehi, eza doho nwo ɓei n alijanu yi, wa gmi ɓe nsi n na vingwo, Yesu woi bwa kakashi n eya.<verse eid="MRK 5:1-2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3-4" style="v" pubnumber="3,4" sid="MRK 5:3-4"/> Eza deye ɓei zhin woi sase dna na vingwo nu, wo ɓei n kalai ko a la wo pa n na gmai a ku asunkna fi wo n na pita, wa gbe agma ya wa bma asunkna ya, wa lo wo nya. Zaho to ɓo ikoi wa gyi wo shi m. <verse eid="MRK 5:3-4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 5:5"/>N nyipyeyi n sukwoyi vinya, woi zan dna n na vingwo n na pei woi fi aku, woi sa wohin ya n na kuta yi.<verse eid="MRK 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 5:6"/>She wo ɓei gye Yesu nkpai, wa busi lo wa ce akwo-kwo shi nwo abye.<verse eid="MRK 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7-8" style="v" pubnumber="7,8" sid="MRK 5:7-8"/> Yesu wa daɓo n alijanu yi wa gna, “zafun nukwoi gmiya ɓe” Kwa sawyi n kalai, “Yesu, Shekwoyi iko da Nugun, Ho ye ha zhin mi knihi nu a? Ntu Shekwoyi ɓo, to ga mi wahala m.”<verse eid="MRK 5:7-8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 5:9"/>Yesu wa nya wo ge, ayi ho ge na? Alijanu kwa ci ge, “Begye, ntu ge yi mwa begye fi lo n za deye mi.” <verse eid="MRK 5:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 5:10"/>Alijanu ɓa gyi Yesu wye ge, wo to tnu nɓai nkpai m.<verse eid="MRK 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 5:11"/>Dna sayi mi, a burutu ho ɓei zhi nmwa begye ɓai gyi anyagyi n pe sepa. <verse eid="MRK 5:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 5:12"/>Ɓa gyi wye ge, “Tnu yi na burutu yi mi.”<verse eid="MRK 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 5:13"/>Yesu wa ga ɓa gbe. A zafun nukwoyi ɓa kun n za yi mi ɓa lo fyi na burutu yi mi. A burutu yi vinya, ɓa busi shin zhi peyi ɓa kafi ʼla, nuwan shin ɓayi.<verse eid="MRK 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 5:14"/>A burutu da busi lo a kauye ɓai wu lafiya, aza yi knuɓe ɓai gye n ɓahin yi. <verse eid="MRK 5:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 5:15"/>Safyewyi a-za ye-zhi n mwa aba Yesu ɓei gni nyi. Ama shi ɓa ɓei gye zayi sase ma Yesu dna n wohin hankali, ɓa wo dna. <verse eid="MRK 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 5:16"/>Aza n ɓa ɓei gye ɓo kwo ɓei zhin, ɓa wu lafiya laɓa. <verse eid="MRK 5:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 5:17"/>Aza ya Yesu wye-gyi ge, Wo lo wonya Wa faɓa. <verse eid="MRK 5:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 5:18"/>Wa je eya lo. Eza wo ɓei na lijanu yi nyi, wa gyi Yesu wye ge wa knulo n Woi. <verse eid="MRK 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 5:19"/>Yesu wa ciwo ge awo, “Lapyi da ha nugundo ho gna ɓa nya Shekwoyi ku zhin ho, shi wo sun-sun gyei lo jesun.”<verse eid="MRK 5:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 5:20"/>Wa ya azhi ngnu awo vi (Dikapolis kni) woi gna za aɓo adnagmayi n Yesu wa zhin wo, ca wo aza n mwa.<verse eid="MRK 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aɓo Wo-woyi Kagna Nya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 5:21"/>Sa Yesu ɓela pi ola ya n ʼya yi, aza yezhi n wo aba n mwa n ʼla gbe.<verse eid="MRK 5:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 5:22"/>Aduwa nyakun tukwoda ɓe, ai yiwo ge Yairus, wa ɓe wa yashi n Yesu abye. <verse eid="MRK 5:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 5:23"/>Woi gyi wo wye ge? Wo kawo nyignu gna, “Wola ga fyi, mi gyi Ho wye, ɓe Halo Ho tuwo Ho bwa wa ka gna.”<verse eid="MRK 5:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 5:24"/>Yesu wa viwo lo, aza viwo na vun. <verse eid="MRK 5:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 5:25"/>Dna na za nɓa ɓei viwo nyi, nyikwoza ho ɓei dna n nyasan-yi aye awo-cei-aba ami yi zewo ya. <verse eid="MRK 5:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 5:26"/>Wo ɓo ku wahala sin woi wu agyiwyeya n mwa n na shigbe-da aba, ama to wa kagna m, sai koyi gya bye-abye nu. <verse eid="MRK 5:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 5:27"/>Wo ɓei ku wo aɓo awo-woyi n Yesu zhin, cenu ɓei zhin wa viwo na vun dna deji, wa towo ʼje bwa.<verse eid="MRK 5:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 5:28"/>Ntuge wo ɓei zhin nubo fyi wo mi, “N ma towa ʼje bwa kawai, mi ɓa kagna.” <verse eid="MRK 5:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 5:29"/>Shi wo ɓei to wo ʼje bwa n kusun, wa ze kagna yi, o wami-zeya zan n sayi-sayi yi, waku wonya kpege wola kagna bwa!<verse eid="MRK 5:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 5:30"/>Yesu wa kpe n sagmanyi ge kagna iko la gmi n Wo, Wa pmi awye shi aza Wa cige, “Nyika to mi jekpe bwa?”<verse eid="MRK 5:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 5:31"/>Owo abara nya Wo ge, “Aza n ɓa sheho kna zhl mwa nyi, Hoi gni Hoi nyaɓo ge nyika to Ho bwa?”<verse eid="MRK 5:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 5:32"/>Ama Wa ce Wa sha-wye laɓa n ʼna bai Wagye ʼza n wa to Wo bwa. <verse eid="MRK 5:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 5:33"/>Nyikwo-za ho, shi wo ɓei gye ɓo kwa zhin wo, wa ɓe n dnayi, woi vin, wa cakwo-kwo shin Wa bye wa gna Wo ɓo wa zhin. <verse eid="MRK 5:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 5:34"/>Wa gna wo ge, “ho gaiciya ga, kwo la ho kagna, lo ho nya n lafiya yi.”<verse eid="MRK 5:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 5:35"/>Woi ye gni Woi daɓo n woi atnu-tnu yi ɓa ɓe ɓai kun n Yairus puwa ge esa la diya, owo nyigun lafi, apma to lo Yesu wa shan lom. <verse eid="MRK 5:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 5:36"/>Ama to Yesu wa gye wo anuwan n ɓa ɓeda yim, waci Yairus ge, “To wo dnam, la gaiciya ga Mi.”<verse eid="MRK 5:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 5:37"/>Yesu wa kpe a za zhi n bmi to wa ye ge ɓa lo api min; akpe Bitrus, n Yakubu yi, n Yohanna yi. <verse eid="MRK 5:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 5:38"/>Sanu ɓa ɓei lofi ɓa gye aza fi ɓai cibwi, ɓai ɓewyi, har ɓaku jeje. <verse eid="MRK 5:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 5:39"/>Wa lo mi, Wa daɓo na zayi, “Knihi nu zhin fyei cibwia? Eɓi to fim, wo wangye nu kawai.”<verse eid="MRK 5:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 5:40"/>Ɓa mawo san wyegbaci nya, ama Wa gnaɓa ge ɓa la kun. Wala ɓiyi ʼya nwo dadayi n Wa barayi ɓa lolo nyakun mi n ʼɓiyi ɓei yadna nyi.<verse eid="MRK 5:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 5:41"/>Wa ta bwa shi wo nbwa, wa ci ge, ɓinyikwoi lakala. (Owo aye ɓei nyi awo-cei-aba nu) <verse eid="MRK 5:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 5:42"/>Wa lakala gni-agni, wa ya zan-zan, ce awo owo azamayi. <verse eid="MRK 5:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 5:43"/>Yesu wa tu ɓa gbe n kala yi ge, ɓa to ye zaho-zahoi wa kpe cem. Wa gna ɓa ge ɓa ga ɓinyikwoyi hi nyagyi.<verse eid="MRK 5:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="MRK 6"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 6:1"/>Esa fyewyi wa fa ekni dehi, wa O jeze lo wo ayi Nazarati ɓedo nwo abara yi. <verse eid="MRK 6:1"/><verse number="2-3" style="v" pubnumber="2,3" sid="MRK 6:2-3"/> N satiwyi yi wa lo aduwa nyakun, ntu ge wo wu nya, owo ɓeyekpe nwo aɓo wo-woyi zhin yi kwa wo aza, ntu ge wo ɓo zhin oza nu ngye ɓa. “Ɓa nya ge kafinta n Maryamu yi nugun nu to n, owo azaje nu to n Yakubu yi n Yusufu yi n Yahuda yi ɓedo n Simani yi n? Owo amapwi to bwa gni fi lo n ya n yi n.” To ca da ɓa m.<verse eid="MRK 6:2-3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 6:4"/>Yesu wa ci ɓa ge “Anabi n mwamwa yi nna baho-baho yi, sai dai n wohin ayi nwo aza aba.” <verse eid="MRK 6:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 6:5"/>Ntu ɓa tna gaiciya ga ɓo, wo to ɓo mi wa zhin aɓo wo-woyi nɓa aba m, sai dai wo ɓo to anyasan yi bwa, wa ka ɓa gna. <verse eid="MRK 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 6:6"/>Ca wo wo ntu ɓa tna gaiciya ga ɓo. Wa gmiya wa lo azhi do wa wu ɓa nya. <verse eid="MRK 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 6:7"/>Wa yi awo-cei-aba, wa tnu ɓa ngun aba-ba, wa ga ɓa iko tu nna azafun nukwoi tukwo. <verse eid="MRK 6:7"/><verse number="8-9" style="v" pubnumber="8,9" sid="MRK 6:8-9"/> Wa gna ɓa ge ɓa to la nyahon, sai oɓa busi zanzan nya. Ɓa to la nyagyi n pwakun yi ko agywye ko abuada do ko eje do m.<verse eid="MRK 6:8-9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 6:10"/>N fya lo ezhi fya ku bwa fi n puwa gmanyi har fya kun n zhihi. <verse eid="MRK 6:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 6:11"/>N fya lo ezhi nna to gwo fye ko a kna fya ɓeda tnubuan m, fya abwitukun luya nfye apita, fya kun, fya fa ɓa nɓa aɓoi.<verse eid="MRK 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 6:12"/>Owo abara ɓai gna zaho-zahoi nɓa gye, n ge wo la laifi fa. <verse eid="MRK 6:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 6:13"/>Ɓa kun alijanu ya n mwa, ɓa ka anyasan yi gna, ɓai shin ɓa zaitun mi.<verse eid="MRK 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Yohanna Fi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 6:14"/>Esa fyewyi Hirudus wa wo Yesu nabari, ntu ge a ɓei zhin ai da wo aɓo wo-woyi zhin ɓo abaho-bahoi. Esu wa zhin nubo ge ko Yohanna batizma zhin yi nu la laka n vigwo. Aza ci ge ashe ce nu zhin woi mi woi zhin aɓo wo-woyi. <verse eid="MRK 6:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 6:15"/>Azadoho ɓai gye ge Yesu zhin Iliya nu, ko anabi kwoi-kwoi ho nu la laka n vingwo. Azadoho ɓa gye ge anabi woi-woyi ho nu ngye anabi dnagmayi ho.<verse eid="MRK 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 6:16"/>Hirudus wa ci ge awo, “Yohanna nu eza nmi ɓei la wo tukwo zunya, wola laka n vingw.”<verse eid="MRK 6:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17-18" style="v" pubnumber="17,18" sid="MRK 6:17-18"/> Ntu ge Hirudus ɓei la Yohanna wan, wa wo dna n kurkuku, ntu ge wo ɓo zhin woi gna wo ge kwo to bmiya lo wa la Hirudiya owo zado Filibbus nyikwo m. <verse eid="MRK 6:17-18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 6:19"/>Hirudiya ɓo cei pma a Yohanna wu, ama wo to ɓo mi wa zhin lo nu to Hirudus woi ye m. <verse eid="MRK 6:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 6:20"/>Hirudus ɓei zhin woi ga Yohanna mwa-mwa, woi kpe ge wo zhin oza befyecei nu nza gyi-gyi-yi, wa wo kna. Wo ɓei zhin woi ye wa wo Yohanna ɓeda, ama shi wo ku wo kwa gna wo gna-gna nwo mi.<verse eid="MRK 6:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 6:21"/>Hirudiya sa ɓewo Hiridus mama nyipyeyi kwa shegundo wa yi aza agmada zhin n wo puwa, owa bmazhinyi, asoja tukwoda, n na za dnagmai yi n ɓa knu Galili. <verse eid="MRK 6:21"/><verse number="22-23" style="v" pubnumber="22,23" sid="MRK 6:22-23"/> Hirudiya nyrgnu wa nya-nya nɓa bye har kwa da ɓa gma vinya. Esu wa zhinwo alkawali ge ntu onya ɓo nwa nya nyi, wo ɓa gawo nyahonyahoi n woye. “Kwo emi kni, ma gna kwaje ma gaho tokun yi.”<verse eid="MRK 6:22-23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 6:24"/>Wa gmiyalo wa nya wo ʼya, nya kwo bmiya wa nyaɓo. Owo ʼya wa gna wo ge, “Lo ho gna ho ye Yohanna Baptisma zhinyi tukwo nu.”<verse eid="MRK 6:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 6:25"/>Wa je zelo osu aba npye wa gna woge, “Miye Yohanna Batisma zhin yi tukwo n sayiye tu n fintala.”<verse eid="MRK 6:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 6:26"/>Kwa gna esu gna-gna, ama kwa wo-wo shan n wo ɓa bma wo alkawali ya na ʼza bye nyi. <verse eid="MRK 6:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 6:27"/>Wa tnu wo guyi ge, wo lo wo ɓe n Yohanna tukwoyi. Soja yi, Wa lo kurkuku wa zun Yohanna tukwo. <verse eid="MRK 6:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 6:28"/>Wa ɓe ceyi shi ntu fintala, wa ga ɓinyikwoyi wa lo wo ʼya ceyi.<verse eid="MRK 6:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 6:29"/>Sa n Yohanna bara ɓei wo nya kwa zhin, ɓa lo ɓa la Yohanna nahi ɓa bikwo dna vingwo.<verse eid="MRK 6:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 6:30"/>Yesu a bara jezeɓe waba ɓa gna wo a tnu-tnu vinya ɓa zhin n nyayi n ɓa gnaza nɓa ɓei lo ɓa aba nyi.<verse eid="MRK 6:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Wa Ga Aza Dubu Ngun Atnu Nyagyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 6:31"/>Nnavun Yesu wa gna ɓa ge ɓa kuka naza ʼba ɓalo ɓa ku sun, ntuge aza mwa-begye ɓai ɓe ɓai lo, to ɓa bwasa ɓa gyi nyagyi m. <verse eid="MRK 6:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 6:32"/>Ɓa kuka fi n ʼya ɓa lo abado n ɓa ɓei wo pyipyi-pyi <verse eid="MRK 6:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 6:33"/>Ama aza mwa begye ɓa ku gye ɓai lo, aza she ɓa kpe ɓa busilo ɓa sun ɓai, ɓai kazhi n ʼya. <verse eid="MRK 6:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 6:34"/>Aza yezhi shi ɓa zhin ɓa shin yezhi, kafin wo kashi n ʼya. Wa gye ɓa sun-sun n tuge ɓa ɓei zhi n gye akni n ɓato knayi yim, Wa wuɓa anya mwa begye n kwo ɓei bmiya ɓa kpeye. <verse eid="MRK 6:34"/><verse number="35-36" style="v" pubnumber="35,36" sid="MRK 6:35-36"/> Nwyesheyi, owo abara ɓa gna wo ge, “Gna aza ɓa lo ezhi ɓiyi ɓa si nyagyi, n tuge nyagyi to lo n bmana ye a gyi m, sukwo nyi bwa ɓe-ɓe nu.” <verse eid="MRK 6:35-36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 6:37"/>Ama Yesu wa gnaɓa ge, “fye ga ɓa nyagyi,” Ɓa cige, “N kni nyi ya? Ntuge kwo ɓa dnaɓo za mi wa si nyagyi ga za n mwabegye layi.”<verse eid="MRK 6:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 6:38"/>Yesu wa nyaɓa, “Yi nyagyi shi lo mwa? Fye lo fye kpe ge-nyi.” Ɓa jeze ɓe ɓa gnawo ge, “Bredi lo ngnu atnu n na wyesala yi ngnu aba.” <verse eid="MRK 6:38"/><verse number="39-40" style="v" pubnumber="39,40" sid="MRK 6:39-40"/> Yesu wa gna aza ge ɓaku sase, safyewyi aza sase zhi shitnu-shitnu, tagyi-tagyi kpe na gbe-gbe. <verse eid="MRK 6:39-40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 6:41"/>Wa ku bredi ngnu atnu ho, n wyisala ngnu aba hi Wa kpe wye wushe Wa zhin godiya ntu nyagyi ɓo. Wa gna wa bara bredi n na wyisalayi ɓa gnaza. <verse eid="MRK 6:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 6:42"/>Aza gyi har nubo kwa fuɓa, to ɓa shan mi gyi m.<verse eid="MRK 6:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43-44" style="v" pubnumber="43,44" sid="MRK 6:43-44"/> Aza ɓei nyi dubu ngnu atnu (5,000) n ɓa ɓei gyi nyagyi nyi, n na vun a ye awyiwoyi zhi, a ceknu awocei-aba. <verse eid="MRK 6:43-44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 6:45"/>Nsayi Yesu wa gnawo abara ge ɓa lo ʼya ɓa jezelo Basaida Wa kmaɓe daɓa. Wohin woɓa cegni wa gna za mi.<verse eid="MRK 6:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 6:46"/>Ndeye avun wa lo epe wa zhin aduwa. <verse eid="MRK 6:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 6:47"/>Nsukwoyi owo abara yi fi n ʼya, n kpe n ʼla tasin, woi ce tu nkma n Wo gmanyi yi. <verse eid="MRK 6:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 6:48"/>Wa gye ɓa fi n wahala dnagmayi ɓai gye azhin a nuwan dokwo yi, n ʼseyi, Wa zan-zan lo da ɓa tu nuwan ʼshe har Wa ya ɓa diya. <verse eid="MRK 6:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 6:49"/>Ama shi ɓa ɓei gye nyaho kwoi zan-zan lo n ɓa bmayi, ɓa fyaku n dnayi ɓai gye ge nya-subwi nu. <verse eid="MRK 6:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 6:50"/>Ɓa ku gyewo vinya. Wa daɓo ɓai n sagmanyi yi, “Emi nu! Fye to wo dna m!” <verse eid="MRK 6:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="MRK 6:51"/>Wa lo ʼya daɓa ese kwa ce pyi-pyi-pyi. Ba sase fi n ʼya to ɓai mi ɓedam. <verse eid="MRK 6:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="MRK 6:52"/>Har sayi ye, ɓa to ɓei ye kpe Wo ye, du na ɓo awo-woyi n Wo ɓei yi ku zhin nwyeshe yi nyi, ntuge ɓa to ɓei cei pma ɓa ga gaiciya m.<verse eid="MRK 6:52"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="MRK 6:53"/>Sanu ɓa ɓo kusi Janisarata kni ɓa kpe eya gni n nuwan gbe. <verse eid="MRK 6:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="MRK 6:54"/>N wo kakashiyi, aza n ɓa ɓei zhi nabayi, ɓa kpewo ye n sa gmanyi yi. <verse eid="MRK 6:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="MRK 6:55"/>Ɓa busi laɓa ɓai gna ʼza ge Yesu laɓe, ɓa ya anyasanyi ku lowo ceyi kpe na pece. <verse eid="MRK 6:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="MRK 6:56"/>Esa n Walo a kauye, n na zhi yakwo yi, n na fwa yi, ɓa ku a-nyasan yi lo wo cei na zokwo n na gnikwo bayi, ɓa yi wo wye ge wo fwa ɓa towo ejekpe bwa kawai shi a za ɓei to wo bwa n sun ɓa bwa kagna.<verse eid="MRK 6:56"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="MRK 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Akunnu Tukwoda Ɓa Nya Yesu Aɓo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 7:1"/>Nwyihoi a Yahudawayi adini tukwoda ɓa knu Urushelima ntu, ge ɓa dna Yesu wye. <verse eid="MRK 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 7:2"/>Ɓa gye Wo j abara ɓai gyi nyagyi to ɓai zhin a Yahudawayi knunun, <verse eid="MRK 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 7:3"/>(Gama a Yahudawayi tun baga a Farisawayi, ɓata gyi nyagyi to ɓai nabwa n na bwagma yi m, shi ɓa knunu kwokwoyi kwo da. <verse eid="MRK 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 7:4"/>Sanu ɓa zhi gnikwo, tilas ɓa zhan ɓahin kpa kafin ɓa gyi nyagyi. Ɓa na knunu ye pya yi lo mwabegye tunyi sapa ɓai zhin ɓa, har naiye ngye aknunu shaknu zhan nya, na kwanu zhan yi.)<verse eid="MRK 7:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 7:5"/>Ntu lonu, adini tukwoda ɓa nya wo ge, “Knihi nu zhin to ho abarayi vi yi aknunu ma? Ntu ge ɓa gyi nyagyi to ɓai nabwa kpam.”<verse eid="MRK 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6-7" style="v" pubnumber="6,7" sid="MRK 7:6-7"/> Yesu wa gnaɓa ge, “Efye amu-nafici da! Ishaya Anabi wa wufye bmi pai-pai sa n wa ci cei ge, ‘Azaye ci Shekwoyi ngbeyi nu, ama ɓa ta yewo n ɓa bugba min. Ɓa gami mwa-mwa gbeloyi nu, ntu ge ɓa gna aza ge Shekwoyi gnage a shi ɓa wyidna bwa. Ishaya da gaiciya nu.’<verse eid="MRK 7:6-7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8-9" style="v" pubnumber="8,9" sid="MRK 7:8-9"/> “Ntuge fye shan Shekwoyi wa do n ye knunu yi. Ɓehin-hin, fye na Shekwoyi owa ɓo nu fye shi fya knunu bwa.<verse eid="MRK 7:8-9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 7:10"/>“She Musa ɓei ga fye gbetu deye n Shekwoyi aba: ‘Gaho dada mwa-mwa nho-yayi.’ Wacige znu wa da ɓeda nukwoyi tu wa zakwoyi tukwo, wo ɓa fyi. <verse eid="MRK 7:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 7:11"/>Amma fya cige, Ɓenukwoi nu ton nza gye wa zakwoyi fyi n san, wa ci ɓa ge, ‘Aiya mitami ma bmafye zhin m, ntu ge nya mi ɓei ɓa ga fye nyi, mi la ga Shekwoyi.’ <verse eid="MRK 7:11"/><verse number="12-13" style="v" pubnumber="12,13" sid="MRK 7:12-13"/> N lonu fye bma Shekwoyi awyidna ya n nabai fya shi aknunu bwa n zanyi-koci wa zhin, aknunu ypya lo n mwa begye.”<verse eid="MRK 7:12-13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 7:14"/>Nnavun Yesu wa yi aza ge ɓa ɓe ɓa wo. Wa ciɓa ge, “Efye viyan, fye wo, fya fwa kwa lofye njesun. <verse eid="MRK 7:14"/><verse number="15-16" style="v" pubnumber="15,16" sid="MRK 7:15-16"/> Efya wye-wye tabwa nyasan, ntu nyaɓo fye gyi m, sai nya fye zhin nubo ceyi, fyei da!”<verse eid="MRK 7:15-16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 7:17"/>Navun Wa lolo puwa mi, ntuge Wa lka na za aba, owo abara ɓa nyawo owo ɓeda awyega.<verse eid="MRK 7:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 7:18"/>Fye to na wyegai lo cen, nge nya gyi, konu tatu fye cegye n? <verse eid="MRK 7:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 7:19"/>Gama nyagyi ta siho bugbam, ama kwo diya lo nubo mi. (Owo ɓeda lonu ko wuge nyagyi doho dohoi gyi-gyi-yi.)<verse eid="MRK 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 7:20"/>Wa cige. “Aɓo nubo zhin nukwoyi nu tuza cegye. <verse eid="MRK 7:20"/><verse number="21-22" style="v" pubnumber="21,22" sid="MRK 7:21-22"/> Gama n za bugbanu n na nubo zhin nukwoi knu, nayi dhakpe, eviwyi, zawu, Kwocedna, azanya pwa wo, anagbayi zhin, shewo, ɓonukwoi mwi, akmikni, tukwo mwa, nyaze, na ɓenukwoyi vinya. <verse eid="MRK 7:21-22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 7:23"/>A nya nukwoyi ye vinya knu n ʼzami nu, ɓanu tu za cegye to Shekwoyi wa gwo zam.”<verse eid="MRK 7:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ɓeho-ɓehoyi Nwa Zhin Kwo Zhin Ɓewowoyi Nu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 7:24"/>Nnavun Wa fwa Galili Wa lo Taya kni n Sida yi, to Wa ye a kpe ge Wo la ɓem, ama to kwa zhin m, gama Owo ɓeɓe nabari ɓei la lapwi wolo-wolo she kwo shin zhin.<verse eid="MRK 7:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 7:25"/>Nsagmanyi yi, nyikwoza ho wa ɓe, n na alijanu bei wan wo nyigun. Wo bei ku Yesu nabari wo, wa ɓe wa yashi n Yesu abye. <verse eid="MRK 7:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 7:26"/>Wa gyiwo wye ge wo kawo nyigun gna. (Ama wo ɓei zhin Sirufunikiyi nu “ebye wyegba ci nya.”)<verse eid="MRK 7:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 7:27"/>Yesu wa gnawo, “Kwo bmiya Ma bma ma zanu zhin kpa – a Yahudawayi, kwo to bmiya a la aɓi nyagyi a ga amwi m.”<verse eid="MRK 7:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 7:28"/>Nyikwoza ho wa cige, “a zhin a ga amwi biyi nba zhi n tabul sinta, dna na ɓi nyagyi ba gyi nya kwoce nyi.”<verse eid="MRK 7:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 7:29"/>Wa ciwo ge, “Hada dai-dai! Mi la ho nyigun kagna, lo ho nya. Alijanu la ho ɓi fwa!”<verse eid="MRK 7:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 7:30"/>Sa nu wo ɓei si apyi, wa gye wo ɓi wangye tu n gado, Alijanu yi lawo fwa.<verse eid="MRK 7:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 7:31"/>Wa gmi n Taya W lo Sida, Wa jezelo Galili ʼla n na zhi ngun awo zokwo yi. <verse eid="MRK 7:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 7:32"/>Aɓe Wo n tnubua-gunayi woi san gu-gulo n jesun. Aza vinya ba gyi Yesu wye ge Wo to wo bwa Wa kawo gna.<verse eid="MRK 7:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 7:33"/>Yesu wa gmi wo n na za, Wa lo nwoi Wa dna wo bwanyi n tnubua. Wa kni akni kpe n bwanyi Wa to wo nyitala bwa n cei. <verse eid="MRK 7:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 7:34"/>Wa kpewye wu She, Wa ya sun Wa ciege, “Guya.” <verse eid="MRK 7:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 7:35"/>N sayi-sayi yi, wa ya atnubua ɓewo woi da ɓo njesun dai-dai.<verse eid="MRK 7:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 7:36"/>Yesu wa gna aza ge ɓato wu lafiya labam, ama sa n Wa gnaba ge bato dam, ɓa gna dada nu. <verse eid="MRK 7:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 7:37"/>Ntu ge ce bei wo ɓa n mwa. Cici ɓa cige, “Ɓoho-ɓohoi n Wa zhin, ɓo wowoyi nu, har woi zhin a tnubua gunayi n na takpeɓedayi, ɓai daɓo cewo.”<verse eid="MRK 7:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="MRK 8"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1-2" style="v" pubnumber="1,2" sid="MRK 8:1-2"/> Nwyihoi, aza je yezhi n mwa-begye, nyagyi a kuɓa zo. Yesu wa yi Wo abara Wa gna ɓa ge, “Mi gye a zaye sun-sun lo ntu ge, oɓa nyipyei tahi nu nyi naiye nyagyi yi to ye ɓai celo ba gyim. <verse eid="MRK 8:1-2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 8:3"/>Nma tun ɓai n na pyi to ɓai gyi nyagyi mm ɓa ɓa cafyi zokwo. Ntu ge aza lo ɓai knu naba kpai.”<verse eid="MRK 8:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 8:4"/>O wa ɓara nyawo ge, “Yi ɓa bwa nyagyi n zhabui ye a gaɓa ɓa gyi?”<verse eid="MRK 8:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 8:5"/>Yesu wa nya ɓa ge, “Fye n bredi yi shi n gnu a kniya?” Ɓa ciwo ge, “N gnu tnaba.” <verse eid="MRK 8:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 8:6"/>Wa gna aza ge ɓa ku sase zhi kni. Wa go bredi wa sa Shekwoyi ami, Wa sa kwo ya, Wa ga Wo abara ɓa gna za. <verse eid="MRK 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 8:7"/>Awyisala ɓei nyi fyewyi, Yesu wa kuɓa Wa tuɓa anabarka Wa ga Wo abara ɓa gnaza.<verse eid="MRK 8:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8-9" style="v" pubnumber="8,9" sid="MRK 8:8-9"/> Aza vinya, ɓa gyi nyagyi nubo a kuɓa fu. N navun Wa gna ɓami ɓa lo apyi. Aza ɓei yezhi nlo dubu gun anyi (4,000) Sa na ɓei ye awyiwoyi zhi a bwa a ceknu dnagmayi ngun tnaba.<verse eid="MRK 8:8-9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Fye ye Aɓo Wo-woyi Ngun Akninya?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 8:10"/>N sai-sayi Wa lo ʼnwo abara yi ɓa ɓe Dalmanuta kni. <verse eid="MRK 8:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 8:11"/>Sa na Yahudawayi tukwoda ɓei kpe ge Wo la ɓe, ɓa ɓe Wo aba n na bai ɓa na ɓo n woi. Ɓa ciwo ge, “Zhin yi oɓo wo-woyi ya gye! Zhin nyaho kw zhin n nanyi bmana! N na bayi ya gaho gaiciya!”<verse eid="MRK 8:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 8:12"/>Wa do ʼmi n mwa sa Wo ɓei wo lonu wa ciɓa ge, “Mi ta zhin m, fye ye a tnu-tnu a wo-woyi nshan-sun gnu akninya?”<verse eid="MRK 8:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 8:13"/>Wa je eya lo Wa fa ɓa Wa piya lo ola pma deyi. <verse eid="MRK 8:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 8:14"/>Owo abara ɓa ku zamwi to ɓa la nyagyi m, ɓa bwalo n bredi yi shi gmanyi nu n ʼya.<verse eid="MRK 8:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 8:15"/>Sa ɓaɓei lo ɓai pi ola ya, Wa gnaɓa, “Fye zhin peceiye n yeast Esu Hiridus nya n na Farisawayi nya yi.”<verse eid="MRK 8:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 8:16"/>Ɓanya ge, “Wo da kniɓeyi na? Kpekni Wo da bredi nu ɓo n ya zamwi nyi.”<verse eid="MRK 8:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 8:17"/>Yesu wa ku kpe ɓeye n ɓa da, Wa ciɓa ge, “Mi ta da cenun. Fye to kpe ɓo ye nmi dan? Efya bugba dna kala lo nu to fye kpe awyegan?<verse eid="MRK 8:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 8:18"/>“Shi Ishaya da, ʼFye na wyei gyi n wyeba gye ye a tun-tnu a wo-woyi nshan-sun ɓo wye ma? Knihi nu zhin to fyei gu atnubua ya fya wo ɓo ma? Fye ta pa ɓo lo m? <verse eid="MRK 8:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 8:19"/>Aza dubu n gnu atnu (5,000) Mi ɓo fuɓa nubo na bredi yi ngnu 5 nyi ma? Fye ɓo ye apisayi zhi acekun ngnu akninya?” Ɓa cige, “Aceknu awo-cei-aba.”<verse eid="MRK 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 8:20"/>“Esa nmi ɓei kpa aza dubu ngun anyi (4,000) n bredi yi ngun tnaba, knidonu ɓo ce a?” Ɓa cige, “acekun ngun tnaba.”<verse eid="MRK 8:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 8:21"/>“Fyei gye ge Mi damu lo shi fyeto bredi yi shi lon?”<verse eid="MRK 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 8:22"/>Sa ɓa ɓei si Baitsaida, azaho ɓa ɓe n wyebuayi, ɓagyi wo wye ge Wo kawo gna. <verse eid="MRK 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 8:23"/>Yesu wa la wyebuayi yi Wa gmiya gni woi n piwun Wa kni akni kpewo na wye Wa tu wo ɓa bwaya, Yesu wa nya wo ge, “Ho gye nyaho lo sayi?”<verse eid="MRK 8:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 8:24"/>Zahi wa shi awye laɓa wa cige, “E, mi gye azalo, ama mita gyelo dei-dei n, ɓa wulo ngye ashinwa gbigbi nu zan-zan laɓa.”<verse eid="MRK 8:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 8:25"/>Yesu wa tuwo ɓa bwaya njesun, Shi zahi ɓei cewa wye zun, awye kna woya vinya, wa gye nyaho-nyahoi sarai.<verse eid="MRK 8:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 8:26"/>Yesu wa tnu woi nwo aza ʼba. Wa gnawo ge, “To jezelo kauye ho kpam.”<verse eid="MRK 8:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ho Nu Zhin Masifu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 8:27"/>Yesu nwo aɓarayi, ɓa fa Galili ɓa lo Kaisariya Filibi akauye. Shi ɓa ɓei zan-zan lo, Wa nya ɓage, “Aza zhin nubo ge Mi zhin nyikado na? Ɓa dalo gena n Mi tukwoa”?<verse eid="MRK 8:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 8:28"/>Ɓa ciwo ge, “Azaho zhin nubo ge Ho zhin Yohana Baptisma zhinyi nu, aza ho cige Ho zhin Iliya nu, azaho cige Ho zhin anabi sapainya ho nu nwa lakala n vingwo.” <verse eid="MRK 8:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 8:29"/>Wa nya ɓa ge “Fye gyege Mi zhin nyikado na?” Bitrus wa cige, “Ho nu zhin Kristi.” <verse eid="MRK 8:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 8:30"/>Wa gnaɓa ge ɓato gna zaho-zaho yim.<verse eid="MRK 8:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 8:31"/>Wa ya ɓa a wahala gna n ɓa ɓa sun Wo, njesyn a za yakwo, n na prist tukwoda yi, n na Yahudawayi tukwoda yi, ɓa ɓa nawo aɓo, har ɓa wuwo, ama Wo ɓei lakala n vingwo nu anyi-pyei at avun. <verse eid="MRK 8:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 8:32"/>Wagnaɓa ce pei-pei. Bitrus wa la Wo lo ceyi n sepa gmanyi wa gnakni Wo, wa ciwo ge, “Kwo to bmiya Ho da a Be ye pyam.”<verse eid="MRK 8:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 8:33"/>Yesu wa pmiwyeshi Wo abara Wa gnakni Bitrus Wa ciwo ge, “shetan, la pmigni Ma vun. Ho da zanyikwoci ɓeda nu, to ge Shekwoyi nyam.”<verse eid="MRK 8:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 8:34"/>N navun Wayi Wo abara ɓedo n deji yi ge ɓa ɓe ɓa wo. Wa gnaɓa, Fye wo, eza n woye wa vi Mi, wo la anyida yashi wa lami zundu wa vi Mi n bugbayi gmanyi. <verse eid="MRK 8:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 8:35"/>N ho ye ha gni ho wye-wyei, ho ɓa bwi kwo nuwan, Sai aza n ɓa she ɓa wye-wyei ya ntu Mi ɓo, n Nabari manayi yi, ɓa ɓa kpe nyaye na yige wye-wyei bwa.<verse eid="MRK 8:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 8:36"/>Mi gye eza gyiba, wa bwa anyi vinya ama owo wye-wyei kwa bwi dace? <verse eid="MRK 8:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 8:37"/>Nyaho lo ndu ʼza wye-wyei? <verse eid="MRK 8:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 8:38"/>Eza nwa womi vinyikwo n Mi nabari yi dna na nyipyei nukwoyi ye tna gaiciya ga nya, Emi, Kristi, sa Mi ɓei jeze ɓe dna Mi Dada mwamwa n na malalka gyi-gyi-yi Mi ɓei wo zahi vinyikwo ce.<verse eid="MRK 8:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="MRK 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Dna Nwo Mwa-Mwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 9:1"/>Yesu wa godu Wa gna Wo abara ge, “Aza zhilo ya nfye mi nɓata fyi m, sai ɓa gye Shekwoyi bemi kwoi ɓe dna ko ikwo yakwo kpa.”<verse eid="MRK 9:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 9:2"/>Anyi-pyei tnanyi, navun Yesu wa la Bitrus, n Yakubu yi n Yohanna yi ɓa gnulo epeshe. Zaho to ɓei shan knusun n ɓa yim safyewyi Owo awyeba ɓa shando ɓai bmiyana. <verse eid="MRK 9:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 9:3"/>Owo aje ɓai bmiyana n bui-bui yi pesheu n du anyi nya zhin dohodohoi n fwan-fwan. <verse eid="MRK 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 9:4"/>Safyewyi Musa n Iliya yi ɓa ɓe ɓa ya ɓeda n Yesu yi.<verse eid="MRK 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 9:5"/>Bitrus wa cige, “Male, ɓeye bmiya lo mwa. Yi ɓa kpe alubui ngnu ata ntu fye ɓo vinya.!”<verse eid="MRK 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 9:6"/>Wo ɓei da deye ntu ge wo to ɓei kpe ɓeye n wo ɓa shan dan, ɓa ku ɓa nya fyiya zhi n dnayi. <verse eid="MRK 9:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 9:7"/>Ama sa nwo ɓeye daɓo nyi, enyi kwa tuɓa fun kwa gu nyipyei, begye kwa gmi ʼshe, “Emi Nugun ye-yei nu nyi, fye wo wo.”<verse eid="MRK 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 9:8"/>Safyewyi ɓa shawye to ɓa gye Musa n Iliya yim, ɓa gye Yesu nu bwa cegni nɓai.<verse eid="MRK 9:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 9:9"/>Sanu ɓa ɓei kazhi ɓe ʼpe hi, Wa gna ɓa, “Fye to gna za oɓo fya gyen sai Mila laka n vingwo fya ɓei kpeda.” <verse eid="MRK 9:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 9:10"/>Ɓaku kwo shi fyi ɓami, ama cici ɓai dace ɓahin-ɓahin, to ɓa bwa ɓo wyega n Wo da ge, “Kalala vingwo nyi m.”<verse eid="MRK 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 9:11"/>Ɓa ya Wo aɓo nya na Yahudawayi adini tukwo-da zhin ɓa da nge tilas Iliya jezeɓe kpa (Masihu wa kpeanyi ɓe). <verse eid="MRK 9:11"/><verse number="12-13" style="v" pubnumber="12,13" sid="MRK 9:12-13"/> Yesu wa ya ɓeda Wa cige, “Tilas nu Iliya ɓe wa zhin zokwo kpa ɓehin-hin, wo la ɓe ama aza to zhin wo ɓo nbmiya m, ɓa wu wa nyi shi anabi ɓei da. Yesu wa nyaɓa ɓo na anabi ɓei da n Kristi tukwo ge Wo ɓa sin wahala n vinyikwo yi.”<verse eid="MRK 9:12-13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Wa Ka Oɓi Gna</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 9:14"/>Sanu ɓa ɓei kazhi n ʼpe ɓa gye aza yezhi n mwa begye ɓai na ɓo n Wo abara yi ciwa-gmanyi n ɓa ɓei cezhi nyi. <verse eid="MRK 9:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 9:15"/>Aza shi Yesu awye n dnayi shi Wo ɓei kashi ɓe ɓa bayi cewo, ɓa busilo dawo ɓa ɓiwo gna. <verse eid="MRK 9:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 9:16"/>Wa nyaɓa, “Kninya zhin fyei naɓo na je ya?”<verse eid="MRK 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 9:17"/>Zaknayiwa dnaɓe gbe wa cige, “Male, ma ɓe n ɓiyi nu Ha kawo gna, wota milo nɓedan ntuge alijanu dna lo wo mi. <verse eid="MRK 9:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 9:18"/>Osa alijanu lawo kala, kwa lawo kwa zunwo ʼkni. Wa pu-afugya woi gyanyikna wa fyi-fyiya. Ntu lonu mi-i gyi Ho abara wye ge ɓa kawo gna, to ɓai min.”<verse eid="MRK 9:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 9:19"/>Yesu wa gna Wo abara, “O, a gaiciya ga ɓiyi da, Har kniwyi nu Mi ɓa knusun fyei ya? Har kni sayi nu Mi ɓa zhin ankuri n fyei ya? Fye ɓe Mi ɓihi ya.”<verse eid="MRK 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 9:20"/>Ɓa ɓe n ɓihi, ama sa nu wo ɓei gye Yesu, zafun nukwoyi kwa lawo n kalayi kwa zun wo kni wa pu afugya woi gyi anyikna.<verse eid="MRK 9:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 9:21"/>Yesu wa nya wo dada ɓo ge, “Kwo ɓei yawo n kni sayiʼa?” Wa ci wo ge, “Tunyi woi ye bwasun ciwyi. <verse eid="MRK 9:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 9:22"/>Zafun nukwoyi ye zhin kwa zhin wo wa miya fyi ena, n nuwan yi, n nabai kwa wu wo. O, gye yi sun-sun Ha kawo gna n gye Ho ɓa mi.”<verse eid="MRK 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 9:23"/>Yesu wa nyawo ge, “Kninu zhin hoi cige, ngye Mi ɓamiʼa? Nyaho-n yahoi to dnaɓom, hoi ya ga gaiciya m.”<verse eid="MRK 9:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 9:24"/>Owo dada cige, “Mi n gaiciya gai lo, bmami zhin ma bwa kwo mwa.” <verse eid="MRK 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 9:25"/>Sa Yesu ɓei gye aza ɓai yezhi Wa gnakni zafun nukwoyi. “O, Zafun nukwoyi atnubua gunya n takpeɓedanyayi bi ɓe n ɓi yemi, to ha jewo lo m.”<verse eid="MRK 9:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 9:26"/>Zafun nukwoyi ho kwa sawyi kwa pmikwa la ɓihi kwa zun wo kni n mwa n jesun, kwa fawo sayi. Eɓihi wa shiɓo ngye wola fyi har aza cige, “Wo la fyi.” <verse eid="MRK 9:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 9:27"/>Ama Yesu wa shiwo bwa Wa lawo kala gni na gni, Wa wo wola lafiya bwa. <verse eid="MRK 9:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 9:28"/>N navun sanu Yesu ɓei gni n Wo gmanyi yi n Wa bara yi ɓa nya Wo bo, “Knihin na zhin to yi mi n zafun nukwoyi gmiya ma?”<verse eid="MRK 9:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 9:29"/>Yesu wa ciɓa ge, “Aɓo ye pya sai fya zhin aduwa.”<verse eid="MRK 9:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30-31" style="v" pubnumber="30,31" sid="MRK 9:30-31"/> Sanu ɓa ɓei fwa ekni deyi, ɓa zan-zan fi n Galili kni to Wa ye ge aza gye wom n na bayi Wa bwa sa n wo abarayi Wa wu ɓa nya. Wa ci ɓa ge, “Emi, Kristi, aɓa knu Mi a wu Mi ama Miɓei laka n vingwo n na anyipyei ata vun.”<verse eid="MRK 9:30-31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 9:32"/>Ama to ɓa bwa awyegam har odna wo ɓa to ɓa nya Wo kwa wyegam.<verse eid="MRK 9:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 9:33"/>Ɓasi Kafarnahum, Sanu ɓa ɓei ku si puwa n ɓa ɓei fi, Wa nya ɓa ge, “Fye ɓo da kni ɓei nu n zokwa?”<verse eid="MRK 9:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 9:34"/>Ama vinyikwa ku wan ɓa to ɓa dnaɓo gbem, ntuge ɓa ɓei ɓe ɓai naɓo nu najei eza nwo zhin zadnagmai n ɓa mi.<verse eid="MRK 9:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 9:35"/>Wa sase Wa yiɓa zhi nwo aba Wa ciɓa ge, “Eza nwo ye wa zhin zadnagmai tilas wa ze fyenu.”<verse eid="MRK 9:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 9:36"/>Nsayi Wa ɓe nɓiyi dna n ɓa tasin Wa la ɓihi she Wa ci ɓa ge, <verse eid="MRK 9:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 9:37"/>“Eza n wa ye na ɓiyi ngye za deye dna Miye, wo ye n Miyi nu. Eza n wa ye n Miyi, woye n Mi Dadayi nu n Wa tnu n Miyi nyi.” <verse eid="MRK 9:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 9:38"/>Owo bara, Yohanna, wa ci wo n wyihoi ge, “Male, ya gye zaho woi zhin ampanyi n Ho yeyi, woi knu alijanu ya, ama ya ciwo ge wo lafa ntu ge wo to zhin Ho bara nu n gye yim.”<verse eid="MRK 9:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 9:39"/>Yesu wa gna ɓa ge, “Fye to hana n woyim, gama eza to lo wa zhin atnu-tnu wo-woyi dna Miye wa pmi a vun wu, wa zhin gaba n Miyi n pye-pyeyim. <verse eid="MRK 9:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 9:40"/>Eza nwo to zhin gaba n yi yim, wo zhin yi nya nu. <verse eid="MRK 9:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 9:41"/>Ndei eza ga ho nuwan n kofi yi n tu ge ho zhin Kristi nyanu, wo ɓa bwa lada n mwa. <verse eid="MRK 9:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 9:42"/>Ama ndei zaha zhin zaknayi dna n na ɓiyemi wa ce bonyi gwoma a gyiwo ata wyigwo nya dnagmai dna n begye a shewo ya dna nuwan yakwo mi wa bwi nuwan.<verse eid="MRK 9:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43-44" style="v" pubnumber="43,44" sid="MRK 9:43-44"/> “Nho bwa zhin laifi, la kwo zunya. Gwoma ha sase nyalo-nyalo dna na gmada n bwai gmanyi, aya ci ge a she ho ya dna, n na kota shan wun nyin, nha bwayi gyi ngnu aba. <verse eid="MRK 9:43-44"/><verse number="45-46" style="v" pubnumber="45,46" sid="MRK 9:45-46"/> N ho pita lo n hoi naba nukwoyi, lakwo zunya, Gwoma ha sase nyalo-nyalo n pita yi gmanyi aya cige ho lo anapyi n ha pitayi gyi ngnu aba.<verse eid="MRK 9:45-46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 9:47"/>“Nho wye zhin laifi, ha kwo gmiya. Gwoma ho lo Shekwoyi bemi n wyei gmanyi aya cige oha wye gnu aba gye anapyi. <verse eid="MRK 9:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 9:48"/>Aba n gugurugu to shan zom, ena ce to kwoi shan wun m. <verse eid="MRK 9:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 9:49"/>Aba n na sansan yi gyi aza nyalo-nyalo.<verse eid="MRK 9:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 9:50"/>“Sankpegye dadayi to na ampanyiyim, ndei kwa fa kwo dadam. Kwo ta shan mi kwa da nya hom. Ntu lonu fye to ya fye dadam. Fye sase najei n na gmada yi.”<verse eid="MRK 9:50"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="MRK 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Woi Dna Aɓo Nya-nya Gbe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 10:1"/>Nnavun Wa fa Kafanahum U Wa lo Yahudiya kni n Urdun ʼla yi. Aza a yezhi n mwa shi ɓa zhin ɓa shin zhin, Wa wu ɓa nya shi Wo shin wu. <verse eid="MRK 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 10:2"/>A Farisawayi ho aɓe ɓa nya Wo ge, “ho ɓa ye ge a wu mula?” Ɓa ɓei nya Wo lonu ntuge ɓa pyi Wa gam nu. <verse eid="MRK 10:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 10:3"/>Yesu wa nya ɓage, “Musa ɓo da gena tu mulawu tukwa?” <verse eid="MRK 10:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 10:4"/>Ɓa ci ge, “Wo ɓei gna ge kwo to zhin ɓo nukwoyi num, sai dei za ku wasika mula wu nya ka wa ga wo nyikwo.”<verse eid="MRK 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 10:5"/>Yesu wa nya ɓage, “Knihin nu ɓei zhin Musa wa da lonuʼa?” Mi ɓa gna fye nya kwo ɓei zhin wa da lonu. “Ntu fya bugba nukwoyi kala kpe ɓonu. <verse eid="MRK 10:5"/><verse number="6-7" style="v" pubnumber="6,7" sid="MRK 10:6-7"/> Ama kwoto zhin Shekwoyi zokwo num. Tunyi sapa, Wo ɓei zhin zanu-gbai n nyikwozayi ɓa sase nyalo-nyalo nu n knusun dna mula, ntu cenu eza ɓa fa wo dada n wo ʼya yi, <verse eid="MRK 10:6-7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 10:8"/>Wa nyima wo nyikwo n lonu, ɓa to shan aza gnu aba nu zhin m, ama gmanyi. <verse eid="MRK 10:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 10:9"/>To ʼza gna nyaje n Shekwoyi la cigyidom.”<verse eid="MRK 10:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 10:10"/>Nnavun, sanu ɓa ɓei fi Wa bara yi n puwa ho, ɓa je ɓe n ɓeda yi tu mulawu tukwo.<verse eid="MRK 10:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 10:11"/>“Wa gna ɓa ge sanu ʼza yawo nyikwo wa lado, wo ku anagbai zhin n wa ba. <verse eid="MRK 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 10:12"/>Nyikwoza ce nwa ya wo ɓa, wa se ʼzado, wo ku anagbai zhin.”<verse eid="MRK 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 10:13"/>Nsa doho yi, Anyikwoza ɓe n ɓa ɓiyi n na bai Yesu wa tuba anabarka, Owa bara ɓa nya ɓa ya ge ɓato gna Yesu gna-gna m.<verse eid="MRK 10:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 10:14"/>Ama sanu Yesu ɓei gye ɓo ɓa zhin, to ca dawo m, Wa ci ɓa ge, “Fye fa aɓi nawyi ɓa ɓe Ma ba, gama Shekwoyi bemi zhin ɓa nya nu. Fye to nya ɓa yam. <verse eid="MRK 10:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 10:15"/>Ɓehin-hin nu n Mi gna fye, eza nwo to ɓe Shekwoyi aba ngye ɓi m, ata ye ge wo lo Wo bemin.”<verse eid="MRK 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 10:16"/>Nnavun, Wa kpa bwa na ɓihi tukwo Wa tuba anabarka.<verse eid="MRK 10:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 10:17"/>Sanu Wo ɓei lakala, ʼza doho wa ɓe woi busi wa cha kwo-kwo shi n Wa bye wa nya Wo ge, “Male Manayi mi ɓa zhin knihin nu ma lo sheʼa?”<verse eid="MRK 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 10:18"/>Yesu anya wo ge, “Kninu zhin hoi yi Mi Manayiʼa? Shekwoyi gmanyi nu zhin Za manayi. <verse eid="MRK 10:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 10:19"/>Ama ɓeda n ha nya Mi nyi, ho kpe a wyidna ye lo nge to wu zam, to zhin anagbayim, to ha wyi vim, to ha ceakatam, to ha gyi za fyim, ha ga ho dada mwa-mwa n ho ʼya yi.”<verse eid="MRK 10:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 10:20"/>Zahi wa ci ge, “male, mi shi ɓa bwa vinya, mi to bma doho ya n ɓa min.”<verse eid="MRK 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 10:21"/>Yesu wa wo yeye dnagmai ho tu wo ɓo, Wa ci wo ge, “Nya gmanyi n hoi celo. Lo ho knu ho nyabwa vinya, ha ca gyiwye ha gna a wyekwoyi, ha so ho nyabwa dna n ʼshe, ha ɓe ha vi Mi.”<verse eid="MRK 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 10:22"/>Owa wyeba shando n sayi-sayi, wa lo wo nya to cei dawom, ntuge wo ɓei zhin nyabwayi dnagmai nu.<verse eid="MRK 10:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 10:23"/>Yesu wa shiwo awye shi wo lo, Wa bmiya wye Wa ci Wa bara ge, “Kwo po ɓedna lo nyabwayi wa lo Shekwoyi bemi.” <verse eid="MRK 10:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 10:24"/>Ca woɓa mwa. Yesu wa je ɓa gna: “Ema ɓi yeyeyi, kwo dnaɓo lo eza nwo bugbai shi n nyabwa ba, wa lo Shekwoyi bemi. <verse eid="MRK 10:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 10:25"/>Kwo gna dulo n sauci lakumi kwa Idu na ci buawye, aya cige nyabwai wo lo Shekwoyi bemi.”<verse eid="MRK 10:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 10:26"/>To Wa bara ga ɓedayi gaiciyam, ɓa nya Wo ge, “Ngye nlonu, nyikado nu ɓa shan pwo na nyi ye nto na nyabwai yi nun ma?”<verse eid="MRK 10:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 10:27"/>Yesu wa shiɓa wye zun, Wa ci ɓa ge, “Ntna Shekwoyi, ko ta wo zhin m. Ama n Shewoyi aba, nyahonyahoi to dna ɓom.”<verse eid="MRK 10:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 10:28"/>Bitrus wa ya anya yeyi n wo, n woabara jeyi nku ya ntu Wo ɓo wa cige, “Yi ku anya fa vinya n nabai ya vi Ho.”<verse eid="MRK 10:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 10:29"/>Yesu wa ci ɓa ge, “Wuye Ma gna fye ɓehin-hin eza to lo n wa fa nyaho-nyahoi kwo apyi, owaje, owoamapwi, owoʼya, owo dada, owo aɓi, kwo owo akaya ntu Mi yeye ɓo, har wa gna azaje nabari manayi <verse eid="MRK 10:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 10:30"/>Nwo ta gwo gyiba abwa tagyim, tu nwo puwa, owo aje, owo amapwi, owo ya, owo aɓi, owo kni, nwahala sin yi. Anya deye vinya ɓa zhin wo nya nu, dna na ʼnyi ye n anyi ɓa ɓe lo nyi, njesun wo ɓa bwa wye-wyei nyalo-nyalo nya. <verse eid="MRK 10:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 10:31"/>Ama nmwa begye na gye ge ɓa zhin aza yakwo nsaiye, ɓa ɓei ku ze aza gbagbayi n bwayi. Aza na gye ge, ɓa to zhin nyaho nu yam, ɓanu ɓei zhin aza yakwo n bwayi.”<verse eid="MRK 10:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Wa Da Wo Fi Bo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 10:32"/>Ɓa pmi ɓa lo Urushelima Yesu yi gyi n ɓa bye. Owo abara yi viwo navun, edna ku wan ɓa, Wa lo n ɓai n sepa gmanyi, Wa ya ɓa gna nya n kwo ɓa bwa Wo sanu ɓa si Urushelima.<verse eid="MRK 10:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 10:33"/>Wa gna ɓa ge “Esa yi si ɓo, Emi, Kristi, aɓa wan Mi alo n Miyi n Pirist tukwoda ba wa da Mi efyi wa, wa ga Mi n na Romawayi a knu ɓa wu Mi. <verse eid="MRK 10:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 10:34"/>Ɓa ɓa kpema gye, ɓa kni akni kpe Mi, ɓa gbe Mi ya n ɓa knarufin yi, ɓa wu Mi. Ama n na nyipyei gnu ata avun, Mi ɓa lakala n vingwo.”<verse eid="MRK 10:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 10:35"/>Yakubu, n Yohana yi, Zabedi aɓi, a ɓe ɓa daɓo Woi san-san ɓa ci Wo ge, “yi ye Ha bmayi zhin.”<verse eid="MRK 10:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36-37" style="v" pubnumber="36,37" sid="MRK 10:36-37"/> Yesu wa nya ɓa ge, “Kni do na?” Ɓa ci ge, “Yi cei pmalo yi ye sase viviyi n Hoi n Ho bemi. Zaknayi n Ho bwai-zhe, zaknayi n Ho bwapmi.”<verse eid="MRK 10:36-37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 10:38"/>Yesu wa ciɓa ge, “Fye takpe nya ye lo nfye nyam. Fye ɓa mi fya sin dna Mi kofi liliyi wahala nya n Mi ye Ma sin nyi? Ko a zhin fye batisma n batisma azhin nya yi nkwo zhin tilas Ma zhin nyi?”<verse eid="MRK 10:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 10:39"/>Ɓa ci ge, “yi ɓami.” Yesu wa ci ɓa ge, “Fye ɓa sin dna n Mi kofi azhin fye batisma n Mi batisma yi, <verse eid="MRK 10:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 10:40"/>ama Mito iko yi lo Ma kpe fye viviyi n Ma sese bayi m, n Mi bemi m. A ku ko shiri lu zhin.” <verse eid="MRK 10:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 10:41"/>Sanu Wo abara je ɓei kpe ɓe ye n Yakubu n, Yohanna yi ɓei nya, ɓa gyi minagyi. <verse eid="MRK 10:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 10:42"/>Yesu wa yiɓa Wa gnaɓa ge, “Fye kpelo ge asu n na ʼza yakwoyi na nyi, ɓa wan za sun, <verse eid="MRK 10:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 10:43"/>Ama kwo wulo gbo n fya ba. Zanu n wo ye wa zhin zayakwo n fye mi, tile wa zhin fye bara. <verse eid="MRK 10:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 10:44"/>Eza n wo ye wa zhin zayakwo vinya, dole wa zhin aza bara vinya. <verse eid="MRK 10:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 10:45"/>Ntuge kwo Emi hin, Kristi, Mi to ɓe a zhin Mi bauta num, ama Ma bma aza zhin Ma gami wye-wyei ntu na za gni-gni ɓo.”<verse eid="MRK 10:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 10:46"/>Ɓa ku si Jeriko. Ɓai knuya nu n ʼzhi, aza n mwa begye ɓai viɓa. Nyaɓai ho wyebuayi, ai yiwo ge Batimawus (Timawus ɓi) ɓei sase shi n zokwo gbe, Yesu yi diya.<verse eid="MRK 10:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 10:47"/>Sanu Batimawus ɓei wo ge Yesu diya lo, wa ya wyi ɓe, “Yesu, Dawuda Nugun, gye mi sun-sun.”<verse eid="MRK 10:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 10:48"/>Aza ciwo ge, “La ce pyi!” Ama wa gna wyi ɓe-ɓe. “Aya, Dawuda Nugun, gye mi sun-sun!”<verse eid="MRK 10:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 10:49"/>Sanu n Yesu ɓei wo, Wapi gni n zokwo, Wa ci ge Gna wo ge wo ɓe ya. “Laka ha dagma, wo yi ho lo.”<verse eid="MRK 10:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 10:50"/>Batimawus wa she wo je kwokwoyi ya, wa gmigna, wa lo Yesu aba.<verse eid="MRK 10:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="MRK 10:51"/>Yesu wa nyawo ge, “ho ye Ma zhin ho kninya?” Wyebuayi wa ciwo ge, “Aya, Male, miye ma gye wyeba.” <verse eid="MRK 10:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="MRK 10:52"/>Yesu wa ciwo ge, “Oho gaiciya ga la ho kagna.” Nsayi-sayi yi, wyebuayi wa gye wyeba, wa vi Yesu lo n Zokwo yi.<verse eid="MRK 10:52"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="MRK 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Ɓa Ɓe Urushelima</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 11:1"/>Sanu ɓa ɓei wu vivi n Baifaji yi n Baitanya yi n Urushelima pyifun, ɓa ɓe Zaitun ʼpe Yesu wa tnu Wo abara n gnu aba.<verse eid="MRK 11:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 11:2"/>Wa gna ɓa ge, “Fye lo kauye yi kwo zhi nu. Shi fye ya kwolo, fye ɓa gye zhaci ɓiyi n gyigni n na to shin kwo gnu m, fya lo kwo ɓe Mi ceyi.<verse eid="MRK 11:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 11:3"/>“N zaho anya fye ɓo fye zhin. Fya ci ge, Eyi, Dagayi n kwo ɓei pma lo, Wo ɓa je tnu n kwoyi sa fyewyi.”<verse eid="MRK 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4-5" style="v" pubnumber="4,5" sid="MRK 11:4-5"/> Aza gnu abahi ɓa kuka ɓa lo ɓa gye zhaci gyigni n zokwo n na duba. Sa n ɓa ɓei lokwo ya aza n ɓa ɓei zhiɓo, ɓa nya ɓa ɓo, “Kni nu zhin fyei lo zhaci ɓiyi ya?”<verse eid="MRK 11:4-5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 11:6"/>Ɓa da shi Yesu ɓei gna ɓa ge ɓa da, azahi ɓa ye ge ɓa lokwo.<verse eid="MRK 11:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 11:7"/>Ɓa ɓe Yesu n zhaci ɓiyi yi owo abara ɓa ya ɓa ʼje kpe n kwo boknu Wa gnutu.<verse eid="MRK 11:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 11:8"/>Nnavun, aza ɓa ɓei zhi ɓo, ɓa ya ɓa ʼje zhi n zokwo n Wa bye. A za ho ɓa gbe a bala fintolo ɓa ɓe ncei ɓa ya zhi Wo n zokwo.<verse eid="MRK 11:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 11:9"/>Wo ɓei dna na ʼza tasin nu, aza n Wa bye, aza n Wavun, oɓa vinya ɓai ɓewyi ɓai cige, “Shekwo mwasa n ʼSu yi! Anabarka danu n ʼzayi n Wo ɓe dna n Dagayi ʼye mi!”<verse eid="MRK 11:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 11:10"/>“Anabarka nu n ʼbeyi Wo ɓe ceyi nyi. Eyi dada, Dawuda ʼɓe. Shekwo ngi Esu!”<verse eid="MRK 11:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 11:11"/>She Wo ɓei lo Urushelima, Wa lo aduwa nyakun, Wa shi aba wye laɓa vinya Wa jegmiya, ntu ge nyipyei ɓei la gashin. Walo Baitanya n Wo abara awo-cei-aba yi.<verse eid="MRK 11:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 11:12"/>N labmi yi shi ɓa ɓei fa Baitanya, Wa wo mikun yi gnu Wo.<verse eid="MRK 11:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 11:13"/>Shi Wo ɓei shi awye n Wo abye fyewyi, Wa gye gbayi shinwa gni na fintoloyi ci kpe Wa lo kpekni Wa gye kwo gyi kpe. Ama wa bwa a fintolo nu gye kpe. Ntuge ʼsa to ɓeyi si n kwo ɓa gyi m.<verse eid="MRK 11:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 11:14"/>N sayi Yesu wa tu gbayi hi kni, “Ho ta shan gyi n jesun m.” Owo abara ku wo woi da lonu.<verse eid="MRK 11:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 11:15"/>Sanu ɓa ɓei si Urushelima, Wa lo aduwa nyakun Wa nya aza ya n ɓa ɓei fyi ɓai knu anya fyi na duwa nyakun. Wa ce agylwye shanyi tebul abwa ya. Wa nya a likpe knuyi ya.<verse eid="MRK 11:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 11:16"/>To Wa ye ge zaho-zahoi lo ɓe na kaya knu-knuyi m.<verse eid="MRK 11:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 11:17"/>Wa gna ɓa ge, “Acei ka dna n Litafi, ‘Emi nyakun zhin aduwa zhin ba nu ntu nanyi vinya ɓo,’ ama fye la kwo ze avi nyakun.”<verse eid="MRK 11:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 11:18"/>She a pirist na Yahudawayi tukwodayi ɓei wo nya Wa zhin, ɓa ya shiri zhin she ɓa ba wan Wo. Oɓa wahala gmanyi nu ɓa ɓo wo gyikici dna. Ntu ge aza ɓei n ɓahin yi gagayi da Yesu nya wu ɓo.<verse eid="MRK 11:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 11:19"/>Nwyeshe yi shi ɓa shin zhin, ɓa fa ezhi yi ho.<verse eid="MRK 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 11:20"/>Nlabmiyi, sanu Wo abara ɓei du gbayi hi ya n Wo ɓei tukwo kni nyi, ɓa gye kwo la afintolo woya n ku bwa har agbegye.<verse eid="MRK 11:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 11:21"/>Nsayi, Bitrus wa pa nya Yesu ɓei gna shinwahi n nyipyei avun nya nyi, wa cige, “Male, gyewye, gbayi n Ho ɓei tu kwo kni nyi, kwo ku bwa.”<verse eid="MRK 11:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22-23" style="v" pubnumber="22,23" sid="MRK 11:22-23"/> Wa dna ɓa ɓe gbe Wa cige “Ndei fye n gaiciya gayi lo n Shekwoyi, gaciciya nu Mi gnafye fye ɓa mi fya ci Zaitun ʼpe ge laka ha kadna n ʼla. Tilas kwa vi fye ɓeda. Nya na ye kwonu nyi la gaiciya ga, to ha zhin abugba gnu abam.<verse eid="MRK 11:22-23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 11:24"/>“Fye wo Mi! Fye ɓa zhin aduwa ntu nyaho-nyahoi ɓo, ndei fye ga gaiciya ge fye la kwo bwa, kwo zhin fye nya nu.<verse eid="MRK 11:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 11:25"/>“Ama sanu fye zhin aduwa, zhin eza n ho woi shi bugba gafara nnabai efye Dada n Wo tu she nyi Wa zhin fye laifi gafara ce.”<verse eid="MRK 11:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26-28" style="v" pubnumber="26,27,28" sid="MRK 11:26-28"/> Nsa deye ɓai ku si Urushelima njesun. Shi Wo ɓei zanzan lo n na duwa nyakun ba, a pirist tukwoda n na Yahudawayi tukwoda yi, ɓa ɓe wo aba ɓa nya Wo ɓo “Knihin nu zhin ya? Nyikana ga Ho iko ge Ho nya anyaknuyi ya na duwa nyakun a?”<verse eid="MRK 11:26-28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29-30" style="v" pubnumber="29,30" sid="MRK 11:29-30"/> Yesu wa ciɓa ge, “Mi ɓa dna fye ɓe gbe n fya ga Mi ɓenya ye awyega. Yohanna Baptisma zhin yi ma, Shekwoyi nu ɓei tnu n woi, kwo awo? Fye dna Mi ɓe gbe.”<verse eid="MRK 11:29-30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 11:31"/>Ɓa da kwo ɓahin-ɓahin, “N ya cige Shekwoyi nu ɓei tnu n woi. Wa ci yi ge, ʼKni nyi nu ɓei zhin to fya gwo wo ma?”<verse eid="MRK 11:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 11:32"/>N ya cige Shekwoyi nu to ɓei tnu n woi m, aza tafa yim. (Ntu ge aza ga gaiciya n kalai ge Yohanna bei zhin anabi nu.)<verse eid="MRK 11:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 11:33"/>Ntu lonu ba cige, “yi ta kpe genyi lom.” Yesu wa gnaɓa ge, “Ntu cenu Mi ta ga fye ɓenya amsa cem.”<verse eid="MRK 11:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="MRK 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Anabari N Yesu Bei Da</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 12:1"/>Anyi ɓesisi nyi Yesu ɓei si ga za n sayi-yi. “Zaho ɓo nu aje-mui-fwa, wa nyami ko n Shekna dna mi. Wa ɓwokun nyi ntu na jemui-gma pi ɓo. Wa ofwa wyednai nyakun mi n latu she. Wa pmi wa fwa yadna na haya da kun. Wa laka wa lo kni do n kpai. <verse eid="MRK 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 12:2"/>Sa na jemui-ka sa ɓela si, wa tnu n wo bara yi gmanyi wa gwo odo gawo n kwo ɓa zhin wo nya. <verse eid="MRK 12:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 12:3"/>Ama a fwa daɓa luwo, ɓa jewo zeya lo na bwa gbelo yi.<verse eid="MRK 12:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 12:4"/>“Ofwa da waje tnu n zadoyi, ɓa jewo lu n du za kmisun yi, ɓa tuwo ʼci nukwoyi n tukwo. <verse eid="MRK 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 12:5"/>Eza nna ɓei je tnu n cei nyi, a wo wu, n navun wa tnu na zaje yi, a lu ɓa ai ce ai wu azaho. <verse eid="MRK 12:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 12:6"/>Zaknayi nu ɓei bwa ce owo ɓigba gmanyi. Wa kmatnu n woi, woi gye ge ɓa ɓa gawo mwa-mwa ntu ge owo ɓi nu.<verse eid="MRK 12:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 12:7"/>“Ama sanu afwayi ɓei gye wo woi ɓe, ɓa cige, ‘Owo nu ɓei gyi wo dada fwa ye gado, owo dadayi lafyi. Fye ɓe ya wu wo n nabai ofwa kwa ze yi nya.’ <verse eid="MRK 12:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 12:8"/>Nlonu ɓa wan wo, ɓa wu wo, ɓa she wo nayi ya n fwa ʼkna vun.<verse eid="MRK 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 12:9"/>“Fye gye ge ofwa dagayi ɓa zhin wuna n sanu wa wo ɓo kwa zhan? Wo ɓa ɓe wa wu ɓa vinya wa ga of wa yi na zado akun. <verse eid="MRK 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 12:10"/>Fye ta pa aya ye ba ɓo lo dna n Litafim? ‘Kuta n na nyakun miyi laya, kwonu la zhin bwakwonu yakwo dna nyakun, ai ga kwo mwa-mwa ndu a kuta aje, dna n nyakun yi. <verse eid="MRK 12:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 12:11"/>Deye zhin Dagayi ɓezhin-zhin yi nu, kwoi zhin ɓo wowoyi nu.’ ”<verse eid="MRK 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Anuwunyi Ye Ba Pi Wo Agam</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 12:12"/>A Yahudawa tukwoda ye ɓa wan Wo ntu na ʼnyi ɓesisi ye ɓo. Ɓa ɓei ku kpe ge Wo da ga ɓa nu, ɓan ɓei zhin afwayi anukwoyi dna Wo ɓesisi. Ama ɓa ku wo dna n Wo bwatoyi ntu na ʼza ɓo, ntu ce nu ɓa fwa Wo ɓa lo ɓa nya. <verse eid="MRK 12:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 12:13"/>Ama ɓa tnu na adini n na siyasa tukwoda je yi ɓa daɓo n Woi, ɓai pi Wo agam, n na bai Wa da ɓoho n na ɓa wan Wo n cei.<verse eid="MRK 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 12:14"/>Aza wyekayi ɓa ciwo Ge, “Male, yi kpe ge Ho da gaiciya. Ho ta vi aza ɓemwi, kwo aza ɓo pwa-wom, ama Ho wu Shekwoyi zokwo. Nsayiye, gna yi kwo bmiya a gba gadu n na Romawayi aba, kwo awo?”<verse eid="MRK 12:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 12:15"/>Yesu wa ku gye ɓa awun pi ba, wa ci ɓa ge, “Fye ɓe mi n gyiwyeyi, Mi ɓa gnafye.”<verse eid="MRK 12:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 12:16"/>Sanu ɓa ɓei gawo gyiwye, Wa nyaɓa ge, “Nyikado foto nu tu n yeyi n gyiwye ya?” Ɓa ci wo ge, “Esu nu.”<verse eid="MRK 12:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 12:17"/>Wa gna ge, “kwo bmiya lo a gawo nya kwo zhin wonya. Ama nya kwo zhin Shekwoyi nya tilas fya ga Shekwoyi kwo.” Ɓa gye ɓa tukwo dna n vinyikwo to ɓa kpe ɓeye n ɓa ɓa shan dam.<verse eid="MRK 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 12:18"/>A Sadukiyawayi ɓa yeɓe aza ba ɓa cige, Kalaku to lo n na vingwom. Ba nya ɓo layi.<verse eid="MRK 12:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 12:19"/>“Male, Musa ɓei gayi wyidna ge n ʼza fyi n tna ɓi owo do ɓa lawo nyikwo wa bwa aɓi gawo zado.<verse eid="MRK 12:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20-22" style="v" pubnumber="20,21,22" sid="MRK 12:20-22"/> “To, aza ɓei nyi n gun tnaba, adnagmayi na majei yi. Dnagmayi wa la nyikwo wa fi to woi bwa ɓim. Owo mado wa la nyigbayi ho, ama safyewyi wa fi to woi bwa ɓim. Owo mado wa je wola, sa fyewyi wa je fi to woi bwa ɓim. Har n lonu ɓaku fi vinya to ɓai bwa ɓi n woyin. Nnavun nyikwoyi ho wa wonya fi ce.<verse eid="MRK 12:20-22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 12:23"/>“Nya yi cei pma ya kpe okonu nyi, Dna n Shemi wo ɓei zhin nyikado nyikwo na? Ntuge oɓa vinya zaho to celo n wo to ɓei la wom.”<verse eid="MRK 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 12:24"/>Yesu wa dnaɓa ɓe gbe ge, “Bo kwo gna fye gna-gna nyi, fye ta kpe Shekwoyi ɓeda ye lom. Fyei ta kpe Shekwoyi iko ye lom. <verse eid="MRK 12:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 12:25"/>Sa na zadeye ngnu tnaba n nyikwo-zaye yi ɓei kukala n vingwo, ɓa to ɓei shan mula pam, ɓa ɓei ku ze ngye a malaika nu.<verse eid="MRK 12:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 12:26"/>“Ama tu n kalaku nvingwo ɓo, fye to shin-ba dna n Fitowa tu n Musa tukwo n gbe-gbe nagyi yim? Shekwoyi Wa gna Musa ge ‘Eminu zhin Shekwoyi Ibrahim nya Eminu zhin Shekwoyi Ishaku nya Emiyi nu zhin Shekwoyi Yakubu nya.’<verse eid="MRK 12:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 12:27"/>“Shekwoyi ɓei gna Musa nu ge, aza deye kwo shi kwo nyi sala mwa shi ɓa ɓei fi, ɓaye n wye-wyei lo, ntuge Wo to ɓei cige, ʼMi zhin Shekwoyi aza nya n ɓa to lom! Fye ku bwi aba mwa.”<verse eid="MRK 12:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 12:28"/>Zaknayi n na adini malami ɓei gni ɓo woi wo ɓo ɓa da, wa ku kpe ge Yesu la ɓo dnagbe dei-dei. Ntu cenu wa nya ge, ʼDna na awyidna, kni dai nu zhin dnagmayiʼa?<verse eid="MRK 12:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 12:29"/>Yesu wa dna ɓegbe, “Odo kwa ci ge, ‘Fye wo, O, Israila! Eyi Dagayi Shekwoyi gmanyi nu, Shekwoyi do to shasun m.<verse eid="MRK 12:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 12:30"/>“ ‘Kwo zhin tile nu fya yewo fya bugbayi vinya, n fya wye-wyei yi, nfya kala yi.’<verse eid="MRK 12:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 12:31"/>“Bahi, Tile ha ye ho zado n gye hohin tukwo,” Aɓobwashi ho tolo ndu adeye yam.<verse eid="MRK 12:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 12:32"/>Malami yi wa dnaɓegbe, “Ho ku ɓeda gaiciya nya da n Ha ci ge Shekwoyi bwasun gmanyi nu, zaho to shansun lom. <verse eid="MRK 12:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 12:33"/>Mi-i kpe lo ge, kwo dulo ʼza ye wo n wo bugbayi vinya, nwo ɓeyekpe yi, n wo kalayi, maye n ma zajeyi ngye mihin ndu anyaga-ga n zaɓa ga na duwa nyakun nyi.” <verse eid="MRK 12:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 12:34"/>Sanu Yesu ɓei gye wo “Shekwoyi bemi yim.” N deye avun ɓei shan Wo ɓenya m.<verse eid="MRK 12:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 12:35"/>Nsado hoi, shi Yesu ɓei gni woi wu nya na duwa nyakun ba, Wa nyaɓa ɓeda, “Kni nyi nu zhin efya dini tukwoda fyei ci ge, Kristi ɓa gmi n Dawuda byemi nuʼa? <verse eid="MRK 12:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 12:36"/>Gama Dawuda nwohin tukwo ɓei ci ge, ‘Zufun Gyi-gyi-yi nu ɓei daɓo n womi, sanu wo ɓei ci ge, “Shekwoyi ɓei gna emi Dagayi, sase tu mi bwaizhe bwa sai Ma ze oha nuwuyi oha pita kpenya.” ’ <verse eid="MRK 12:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 12:37"/>Shi Dawuda ɓei la Wo yi ge owo Dagayi, Wo ɓa zhin wo ɓi nwuna?” (Ɓeda yepya, kwada aza, ɓa kna tunbua n pwawo yi mwa.) <verse eid="MRK 12:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 12:38"/>Anya doho nyi n Wo ɓei wuɓa n sa deyi, “Fye zhin peceiye na malami yi. Ntu ge ɓa ye ɓa kpe aje yakwo agyiwye-da nya n na ɓeye-kpei, nnabai aza ɓi ɓa gna ɓai yazhi, ɓai zan-zan na gnikwo ba n nabai a gye ɓa wye. <verse eid="MRK 12:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 12:39"/>Ɓa ye a seseba manayi na duwa nyakun, n na mwa-mwa ba yi, aba na zhin aɓo gmada. <verse eid="MRK 12:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 12:40"/>Ama ɓa gyi anyigbayi fi n ɓa puwa n tna vinyikwo. Ntu ge ɓa takpe ɓa haliyem, ɓa laɓa ngye ɓa gyi-gyi-yi ɓai zhin aduwa kpadala yi n na ʼza bye. Ntu deye ɓo, oɓa tata ɓei la du aza nya.”<verse eid="MRK 12:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 12:41"/>Safewyi Wa lo aba na gwo sadaka nyi n na duwa nyakun, Wa sase tu Woi kawye, woi gye shi aza ya agyiwye fi. Anyabwayi hoi ya agyiwye fi n mwa. <verse eid="MRK 12:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 12:42"/>Safewyi nyigbayi ho wa ɓe, nwo to ɓei nyaho yim, wa ya akobo fi ngnu aba.<verse eid="MRK 12:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43-44" style="v" pubnumber="43,44" sid="MRK 12:43-44"/> Wayi Wo abara wa ci ɓa ge, “nyigbayi, san-yi da yi, n wa ga kobo aba nyi, wo la nya ga n du a gyiwye da ye vinya. Ntu ge ɓa knikni nu ciwyi nɓa nyabwa, ama wa ga enya nu n wo cei kmasun lo.”<verse eid="MRK 12:43-44"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="MRK 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Kun-kun Nwo Wan-Wan Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 13:1"/>She Wo ɓei fwa aduwa nyaknu n wyiyi yi, owo bara ho wa ci Wo ge, “Male, Ho gye anyaknu manayi nɓa mi-miyi lo na kuta yi n safya je nyi.”<verse eid="MRK 13:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 13:2"/>Yesu wa dna ɓe gbe wa cige, “E, shawye hoye nsai bwa. Ko kuta gmanyi, ato ɓei fwa kwo tu ndo shem, akpe agusa.”<verse eid="MRK 13:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3-4" style="v" pubnumber="3,4" sid="MRK 13:3-4"/> Sa Wo ɓei sase tu n Zaitun pe n na wyei ce n Urushelima, Bitrus, Yakubu, Yohanna n Andarawus yi ɓa ɓe fya-a ɓa nya wo. ʼKni sayi nu n na ɓo deye ɓa zhin aduwa nyakun a? Aɓei ku atuze wu na bye kpa?<verse eid="MRK 13:3-4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 13:5"/>Yesu wa gaɓa amsa kpadalayi Wa cige, “Fye to ye Zaho-Zahoi wa dna fye kwo cem. <verse eid="MRK 13:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 13:6"/>Ntuge aza ɓa ɓe n mwa begye ɓai cige ɓanu zhin Kristi, har ɓai dna aza kwoce mwa.<verse eid="MRK 13:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 13:7"/>“A ɓei sun knu vi-viyi n na bayi mwakpa n jesun, ama ʼsa kmaknayi nu to num.<verse eid="MRK 13:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 13:8"/>“Ntuge akni n na ʼbeyi ɓei sunknu n najeyi, ekni ɓei shan-shan n na bayi gbo-gbo, n miknu yi, Azhin ɓiyi nu nyi kwoi wu ge odo n kwo ɓelo nyi, kwo dulo ya. <verse eid="MRK 13:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 13:9"/>Ama sa na nya deye ɓei zhin, fye ye lura, ntugɓe fye ɓe fi n wahala n mwa. Aɓei lo fyei n na wadayi aba. Ai lu fye n na duwa nyakun, ai ga fye laifi n na gwamna ʼba n na suyi, she fye zhin Ma viyi. Efye sa nu nyi nfye ɓei bwa fya zhin emi eye saida nɓa bye. <verse eid="MRK 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 13:10"/>Tila a za wo Nabari Manayi ye n na kni vinya kafin esa Kmaknayj ko ɓe. <verse eid="MRK 13:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 13:11"/>Ama sanu aɓei wan fye alo fyei n na wadayi aba, fye to damu n ɓei n fye ɓa dam, fya bma fyehin. Fye da ɓo n Shekwoyi agna fye ge fye da. Dna sayi mi, efyenu ta daɓom ama Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi nu ɓa daɓo n fyemi.<verse eid="MRK 13:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 13:12"/>“Amajeyi na dnagmayi ɓei knu ɓaje har efi, ada yi knu ɓa ɓi, aɓi yi knu ɓa azakwoyi n nabai a wuɓa. <verse eid="MRK 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 13:13"/>Aza ɓei bmifye ntu ge fye zhin Ma nya nu. Ama eza n wa mi gni har esazo sa to wa na Ma ɓom, wo ɓei pwo.<verse eid="MRK 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 13:14"/>“Sanu fye ɓei gye Nyanukwoi gni a gni-gni na duwa nyakun Nyabai, kna tnubua – busi, n ho ɓa mi ha lo Yahudiya ʼpe <verse eid="MRK 13:14"/><verse number="15-16" style="v" pubnumber="15,16" sid="MRK 13:15-16"/> La pye! Nho tu n nyakun she nu, to kashi ha lo apyi mim. Nho tu fwa nu, to jezeɓe ntu ha gyiwye ɓo kwo ajem.<verse eid="MRK 13:15-16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 13:17"/>“Aya na nuboda ʼba dna na nyipyei ye mi, n na ɓiya yi mɓa na ɓiyi shi. <verse eid="MRK 13:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 13:18"/>Fye zhin aduwa ntuge efye subui to kwoi ɓe dna n vinyikwo mi m. <verse eid="MRK 13:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 13:19"/>Anyipyei a nukwoyi nu na to shin ɓa pya bwam, tunyi shi Shekwoyi ɓei sanyi. Ai ta je ɓa pya bwam. <verse eid="MRK 13:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 13:20"/>N Shekwoyi nu to ɓei ce anyi-pyei a nukwoyi zunyam, wye-wyei gmanyi to ɓei pwom. Ama ntu Wa za kni-kniyi ɓo, Wo ɓei ce anyi-pyei zinya.<verse eid="MRK 13:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 13:21"/>“Njesun n ʼza gna fye ge, Kristi nu gni nyi, ʼKo kuwa ‘Wonu gni nu,’ fye to ye m. <verse eid="MRK 13:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 13:22"/>Ntuge a Kristi akatanya ɓei knu n na anabi akatanya yi n ɓa ɓei zhin aɓo a wowoyi ɓai dna aza kwoce, n kwa yezhi har n Shekwoyi aɓi yi. <verse eid="MRK 13:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 13:23"/>Fye zhin pecei-ye, Miku pma fye gna!<verse eid="MRK 13:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 13:24"/>“N wahala ye avun, nyipyei ɓei dnawyegma, epya to ɓei ga buzangnam. <verse eid="MRK 13:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 13:25"/>Akpasu ɓei kaya, anyi bmana ɓei shando.<verse eid="MRK 13:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 13:26"/>“Nsayi anyi vinya ɓei gye Mi wye, Kristi, Mi yi ɓe dna iko dnagmayi n latuyi ɓe. <verse eid="MRK 13:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 13:27"/>Nsayi, Miyi tnu amalaika ɓai ye Maza ʼkni-kniyi zhi n nanyi mi vinya.<verse eid="MRK 13:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 13:28"/>“Fye tuɓo mwi gbayi shinwa, sanu kwo ya afintolo ci, fya kpege vinyikwo laga.<verse eid="MRK 13:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 13:29"/>“Sanu fya gye aɓo deye n Ma gnafye nyi ɓai zhin, fye ku kpe ge Emi jezeɓe la wo vivi, Mi gnilo n na boknumi gbe.<verse eid="MRK 13:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 13:30"/>“E, anya nyi n ɓa ɓei wuge sak-maknayi la ga. <verse eid="MRK 13:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 13:31"/>Eshe nkniyi ɓa ɓa diya, ama ema ɓeda ta diyan, har nyalo-nyalo.<verse eid="MRK 13:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 13:32"/>“Dudu lonu, zaho-zahoi, kwo amalaika n ʼshe ko Emihin, Mi ta kpe nyipyei yelom, ko esa n na ɓeye ɓei zhin m, akpe Emi Dada n Wo dna she nyi. <verse eid="MRK 13:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 13:33"/>Shi fye ta kpe nyipyei yelo n na ɓeye ɓei zhin nyim, fye ku zhigwu fyei dna Mi ɓeɓe wye.<verse eid="MRK 13:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 13:34"/>“Fye ɓa mwi Mi ɓeɓe do n zayi nwo ɓei lo knido n kpai. Wa ga owa tnu-tnuyi tnu-tnu ɓa zhin wa kpe zhi. Wa gna owo zokwo guyi ge wo dna wo zhi-zhi wye.<verse eid="MRK 13:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35-36" style="v" pubnumber="35,36" sid="MRK 13:35-36"/> “Fye lawye ka dai-dai. Ntuge fye ta kpe saye lo Mi ɓei ɓem. Ko dna sukwo, ko n labmi yi, kwo n nyipyei yi. Fye to ye Miye zhi Ma sun fye zhi fyei wan gyem. <verse eid="MRK 13:35-36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 13:37"/>Oɓo nyi Mi gnafye, n ʼzaho-zahoi yi vinya, Fye gwu!”<verse eid="MRK 13:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="MRK 14"/>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Kun-kun Nwo Wan-wan Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 14:1"/>Paska zhin sa ɓei ce anyi, pyei ngnu aba agmada n na Yahudawayi zhin eyeye, ɓai gyi bredi n tna yist fiyi. A malami adna gmayi n na Yahudawayi atukwoda yi, ɓa ɓei zan zokwo shin shi ɓa ɓa wan Yesu fye-a ɓa wu wo.<verse eid="MRK 14:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 14:2"/>Ɓa cige, “Ama yita wan Wo n Paska sayin, sakun anya lakala dna na za tasin.”<verse eid="MRK 14:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 14:3"/>Yesu ɓei dna n Baitanya kpa, n Siman nayiwun-yi puwa. N na wyeshe nyagyi sa yi, nyikwoza ho wa ɓe n ʼmi nakwoyi kwalba yi shi. Wa kpe koya wa ze ko ya kpe Wo n Wo tukwo.<verse eid="MRK 14:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4-5" style="v" pubnumber="4,5" sid="MRK 14:4-5"/> Azaho n ɓa ɓei gnikpe Woyi na nyagyiba, to ca daɓam, ɓa kwo ze nya wun-ya. Ɓa gna, “Ai kwo ɓo bmiya ha knu emiye na gyiwyei mwa a ga asan-yi.”<verse eid="MRK 14:4-5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 14:6"/>Ama Yesu wa ciɓa ge, “Fye fawo, kninu zhin fyei gna wo gnagna shi wa zhin Mi ɓo manayi a? <verse eid="MRK 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 14:7"/>Fye na san-yi dayi lo mwa n fye yi ɓai yefye bmazhin. Fye ɓa mi fya bma ɓa zhin sanu fya ye cei. Ama safyewyi Mi ta je knusun n fye yin.<verse eid="MRK 14:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 14:8"/>“Wo kuɓo zhin shi wo ɓami, wo ku emi shin Mi nayi kafin Emi bi wyi. <verse eid="MRK 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 14:9"/>Ma gnafye gaiciya, aba vinya n na ɓa zhin Nabari Manayi ye wazi, ɓeye n nyikwoya zhin nyi, aɓa pa ce ai ciwo.”<verse eid="MRK 14:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 14:10"/>N navun, Yahuda Iskariyoti Yesu bara, walo a pirist tukwoda aba wa pagbe nɓai, shiwo ɓa knu Yesu.<verse eid="MRK 14:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 14:11"/>Sa na Pirist tukwoda ɓei wo nya kwa ɓe woyi, ca woɓa, ai daɓanjesun, ɓa zhin wo alkawali ge ɓa ɓa gawo lada, ntu cenu wa ya aba wyedna n sayi n wo ɓa knu Yesu. <verse eid="MRK 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 14:12"/>Ewyi kmisunyi na zhin paska cei nyi ʼwyi na wu a kugya ai zhin hadaya ceyi nyi, O wo abara ɓa nyawo aba n Wo cei pma ɓa gyi paska fi. <verse eid="MRK 14:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 14:13"/>Wa tnu ɓai gnu-aba ɓalo Urushelima ɓa zhin aba shiri. Wa gna ɓa ge, “Shi fyelo, fye ɓo gye zanugbai woi ɓe n nuwan shaknu yi tu, fya viwo. <verse eid="MRK 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 14:14"/>Puwa nwa lo, ‘Eyi gna puwada, ʼFye Dagayi na tnu n yi ya gye nyaknu n ho cei gni, ya ɓe ya gyi paska fi wyeshe yi.’ <verse eid="MRK 14:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 14:15"/>Wo ɓa lo fyei n nyaknu-she-nya dnagmayi n zhanba gni, fye shirya n yi paska yi ɓo.”<verse eid="MRK 14:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 14:16"/>Owo abara n gnu-aba ɓa knuya lo zhi mi ɓa lo ɓa gye nyaho-nyahoyi n shirya gni shi Yesu ɓei gna ɓa, ɓa shirya n paska yi.<verse eid="MRK 14:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 14:17"/>Nwyeshei Yesu wa kma ɓe ngnisun n Wo abara jei. <verse eid="MRK 14:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 14:18"/>Shi ɓa ɓei kpe n tebur ɓai gyi nyagyi, Yesu wa cige, “Ma gna fye, ɓehinhin zaknayi fyemi ɓa knu Mi, Zaknayi n fyemi n wo dnalo ya woi gyi nyagyi Miyi.”<verse eid="MRK 14:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 14:19"/>Bugba wunɓa vinya shi ɓa ɓei wo lonu ɓa ya wo nya gmanyi gmanyi. “Emi nu?”<verse eid="MRK 14:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 14:20"/>Wa dnaɓo gbe ge, “Zaknayi n fye awocei aba mi nu woi gni nyagyi gyi lo n Miyi n sayi ye. <verse eid="MRK 14:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 14:21"/>Tilas Ma fi shi a anabi ɓei da tunyi n sapai, ama, aiya, wahala yakwo shilo n za ba nwo ye wa knu Mi nyi. O! Ngye to aye ma zayim.”<verse eid="MRK 14:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 14:22"/>She ɓa ɓei kpe ɓai gyi nyagyi, Yesu wa la bredi Wa gyi Shekwoyi wye Wa tu kwo anabarka. Wa sakwo ya Wa gaɓa Wa cige, “Fye gyi Emi nayi nu.”<verse eid="MRK 14:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 14:23"/>Wa pmi Wa la kofi Wa zhin Shekwoyi godiya, Wa gaɓa ɓa sin n kwomi oɓa vinya. <verse eid="MRK 14:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 14:24"/>Wa gnaɓa ge, “Ema mi na zeya ntu naza begye ɓo, alkawali woiwoyi nu n Shekwoyi atasin n ʼzanyikwo-ciyi. <verse eid="MRK 14:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 14:25"/>Minu gnafye, Mi taje nuwan shushuyi sin m, sai ewyi Mi ɓei sin odo nkwo kakwo dulo n Shekwoyi Bemi.”<verse eid="MRK 14:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 14:26"/>Ɓa pmi ɓa kwo anyi, ɓa lo Zaitun pe.<verse eid="MRK 14:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 14:27"/>Yesu wa gnaɓa, “Efye vinya, fye ɓa ya Mi, ntuge Shekwoyi ɓo ku da na anabi gbe, ‘Miɓei wu kniknayi, a kni ye busi.’ <verse eid="MRK 14:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 14:28"/>Ama sa Mi ɓei la laka n ʼvingwo, Mi ɓei lo Galili Miyi sun n fyei ɓo.” <verse eid="MRK 14:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 14:29"/>Bitrus wa gna Wo ge, “Ko azaje ya Ho, mida ta ya Hom!”<verse eid="MRK 14:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 14:30"/>Yesu wa cige, “Bitrus, Kafin Pise nugba ɓei ceku bwa bayi nsu n labmi yi, hoi la Ma ɓona abwa-ta.”<verse eid="MRK 14:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 14:31"/>Bitrus wa dnaɓo gbe n kalayi wa cige, “Awo, ko n fi yi, mita na Ha ɓom.” Aza je vinya ɓa bwa da lonu ce. <verse eid="MRK 14:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 14:32"/>Sa fyewyi ɓa si ashinwan nu-nu fwa ho, Ayi kwo ge Jesimani, Wa gna Wo abara ge, “Fye pmi Mi zhi ʼya, Malo Mi zhin aduwa.”<verse eid="MRK 14:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 14:33"/>Wala Bitrus, n Yakubu yi n Yohana yi, ɓa gnilo n Woi. Waya bugba wun n mwa, n kala yi. <verse eid="MRK 14:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 14:34"/>Wa ci ɓa ge, “Emi bugba la wunya har efi, fye ku zhi ya fya gu n gnisun Miyi.”<verse eid="MRK 14:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 14:35"/>Wa ce tala lo fyewyi Wa ca kwo-kwo shi n kni Wa zhin aduwa ge, n gye ko ɓa wozhin, esa nukwoyi nkwo shi wa ʼbye nyi, tokwa ɓem.<verse eid="MRK 14:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 14:36"/>Wa cige, “Dada, Dada nyaho-nyahoyi to dnaɓo Ha bam, la kofi (azhin) ye laya Maba Ama Miye Oho ɓeye nu, to ge eminyan m.”<verse eid="MRK 14:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37-38" style="v" pubnumber="37,38" sid="MRK 14:37-38"/> Wa pmi Wa jezeɓe Owo abara ngnu ata-yi aba, Wa gye ɓaku wangye. Wa yi, “Siman! Fye wangye nu? Ashe Fye ta mi fya gu n Miyi kwo esa gmanyi m? Fye gu ngnisun Miyi, fya-zhin aduwa saknu jaraba-dnayi wa dufye kala. Ko shikwo nyi zafun ceyi yelo, nayi zhin kalagbayi nu.”<verse eid="MRK 14:37-38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 14:39"/>Waje laka lo Wa zhin aduwa Wa gyiwye shi Wo ɓo shin gyi nyi. <verse eid="MRK 14:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 14:40"/>Wa jezeɓe Wa gye ɓai wangye, ntuge aɓeyi ku ɓa ɓe. To ɓa kpe ɓeye ɓa ɓa dam.<verse eid="MRK 14:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 14:41"/>Shi Wo ɓei jezeɓe daɓa bwatayi, Wa ciɓa ge, “Fye wan gye, fye sun! Ama awo, gyewansa ladiya! Fye gye! Ala Mi knu na za nukwoyi aknu. <verse eid="MRK 14:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 14:42"/>Fye ɓe! Fye kukala! Tilas yalo! Gyewye! Emiknuyi laɓe!”<verse eid="MRK 14:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 14:43"/>Nsayi-sayiyi Wo ye gni Woi daɓo, Yahuda (zaknayi n Wa bara) wa ɓe na zayi vi n na knu kaya yi shi, abeyakwo, n na busi gbaknu yi, n na pirist tukwoda n na Yahudawayi tukwo da ɓei tnu ceyi. <verse eid="MRK 14:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 14:44"/>Yahuda ɓei ku gna ɓa, “Fye ɓei kpe ʼza ye nfye ɓa wan, sanu mi ɓei lo mi ɓiwogna miyi powa ʼbwa. Fyeyi wan Wo n ʼsayi n tna ɓednayi.” <verse eid="MRK 14:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 14:45"/>Sanu ɓa ɓei kusi, wa lo Yesu aba wa cige, “Dagayi,” wa shepmawo n gye nugnudo. <verse eid="MRK 14:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 14:46"/>Nsayi laza wan Yesu ɓa Wo shi kpam. <verse eid="MRK 14:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 14:47"/>Ama zaho (Bitrus) wa wa beyakwo wa ka Pirirst dnagmayi bara tnubua ya ceyi.<verse eid="MRK 14:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 14:48"/>Yesu wa nya ɓa ge, “Mi zhin evi yakwo nu fyei ɓe Ma ba n na kun kaya yi shi fya wan Mi? <verse eid="MRK 14:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 14:49"/>Knihin nu ɓo zhin to fya wan Mi dna na duwa nyaknu ma? Mi ɓei dna ɓo Miyi wu nya fyegyi-fyegyi. Ama aɓeye zhin n na bai ɓa nu alɓeda n na ɓei da tu Mi tukwo nu.”<verse eid="MRK 14:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 14:50"/>Nsa deye mi Owa bara yi la busi vinya. <verse eid="MRK 14:50"/><verse number="51-52" style="v" pubnumber="51,52" sid="MRK 14:51-52"/> Ama samari ho ɓei vi ɓa laɓa navun dna na gyewan jekpe. Sa na ʼza ɓeye ɓa wanwo, wa busi, Ko shi ko nyi owo aje ɓo la saya, wa busi n ɓwotolo yi.<verse eid="MRK 14:51-52"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bitrus Wa Na Yesu Aɓo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="MRK 14:53"/>Alo n Yesu yi n pirist yako puwa aba na pirist tukwo da aje nna Yahudawayi tukwoda yi ɓei yefi. <verse eid="MRK 14:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="MRK 14:54"/>Bitrus ɓei viɓa n navun n kpayi wa wyi-ya fya-a wa lo dna pirist Yakwo dugwe wa ce akwo-kwo shi nna naba ɓedo nwa barayi.<verse eid="MRK 14:54"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="MRK 14:55"/>Nmi, a pirist tukwoda, n na Yahudawayi padawa yi ɓai fi ɓai zan Yesu laifi zanyi n ko kunce a zun wo kni a wuwo. Ama to ɓa min. <verse eid="MRK 14:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="MRK 14:56"/>A saida-da akatayi ɓa ɓe, ama ɓa daɓo n gmaje gmi-gmiyi.<verse eid="MRK 14:56"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="MRK 14:57"/>Nkmasun, a zaho ɓa ku kala ɓa ce kata fyiwo ɓa cige, <verse eid="MRK 14:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="MRK 14:58"/>“Yi ɓei ku wo woi cige, ‘Mi ɓa mi aduwa nyakun ya n kwo mi gni n naza ʼbwayi nyi, dna anyipyei gun ata maje odo mi n nato mi n naza abwa yim.’ ” <verse eid="MRK 14:58"/><verse number="59" style="v" sid="MRK 14:59"/>Duddu lonu ɓeda ɓei mbai gmaje gmi-gmiyi.<verse eid="MRK 14:59"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="60" style="v" sid="MRK 14:60"/>Pirist dnagmayi wa laka wa nya Yesu ge “Hota dna ɓe gbe nna da tu nho tukwo nyin?”<verse eid="MRK 14:60"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="61" style="v" sid="MRK 14:61"/>To Yesu wa dnawo ɓegbem Prist yakwo wa nyawo ge, “Eho nu zhin Kristi, Shekwoyi Nugun?”<verse eid="MRK 14:61"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="MRK 14:62"/>Yesu wa cige, “Eminu. Fye ɓei gye mi sase-tu a Shekwoyi bwayi zhe bwa, mi i je ze ɓe anyi dna n mwa-mwa.”<verse eid="MRK 14:62"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="63-64" style="v" pubnumber="63,64" sid="MRK 14:63-64"/> Pirist yako, wa sawo aje ya wa cige, “Yi shan knihi yeʼa? Knihi nu zhin yi pmi a saida-da n shan san? Fye kuwo Wo ɓeda nukwoyi tukwo mwa nya. Fye zun owa ya gena?” Ada viyan ge a wuwo.<verse eid="MRK 14:63-64"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="65" style="v" sid="MRK 14:65"/>Nsayi azaho ɓa ya kni-kni kpewo, ɓa puwo je n nawye, ɓa yawo lu n nawyeba n na knuyi. Ɓai nyawo ge, “nyika na lu hoa, Oho Anabi? Ɓai kpewo agye.” Har ma awadayi atnu-tnu loyi ɓa lo woi ɓai gwo wo apmikni n na wyeba.<verse eid="MRK 14:65"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="66-67" style="v" pubnumber="66,67" sid="MRK 14:66-67"/> Ɓitrus ɓeye dna n dugwe Ɓinyi-kwoyi ho n wo zhin tnu-tnu n pirist yakwo yi wa gye Bitrus shi woi wyena. Wa shi wo awye zun wa cige, “ho ɓei gnisun n Yesu yi n wo gmi n Nazarat nyi.”<verse eid="MRK 14:66-67"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="68" style="v" sid="MRK 14:68"/>Bitrus wa naɓo, “Mita kpe ɓeye lo n ho dam!” Wa gmi ya lo a duba. Safewyi pise nugba ceku.<verse eid="MRK 14:68"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="69" style="v" sid="MRK 14:69"/>Ɓinyikwoyi wa gye wo gni ɓo wa ya azaje gna, “n Wo gni nu! Yesu bara gni!”<verse eid="MRK 14:69"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="70" style="v" sid="MRK 14:70"/>Bitrus wa naɓo n jesun. Safyewyi aza mɓa ɓei zhi nna nawye ba, ɓa ya Bitrus gna, “ho zhin oɓa zanu, ntuge ho gmi n Galilinu!”<verse eid="MRK 14:70"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="71" style="v" sid="MRK 14:71"/>Waya a kmikni woi sinya-si, “Mi ta kpe za deye ye lo nfye zhi fyei dawo ɓe nyim.”<verse eid="MRK 14:71"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="72" style="v" sid="MRK 14:72"/>Nsayi-sayi yi pise nugba ceku, bwa bayi.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 14:72">Nsagmanyi yi wa pa Yesu ɓeda ɓo, “Kafin Pise nugba ceku a bwa aba, ho ɓa namaɓo, abwa-ta.” Wa ya bwici.<verse eid="MRK 14:72"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="MRK 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Owo Wada Nwo Wu-wuyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 15:1"/>N labmiyi, a pirist tukwoda, a byeda, a malami, n na Yahudawayi apadawa yi vinya ɓa kpesa ɓa zhin shawara nyaɓa ɓa zhin. Ɓa zhin shawara ge ɓa tun n Yesu yi dna na soja tasin n Bilatus aba a Romawayi Gomna.<verse eid="MRK 15:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 15:2"/>Bilatus wa nyawo. “Ho zhin a Yahudawayi Esu nu?” Yesu wa yewo ge, “Ho ku da dai-dai.”<verse eid="MRK 15:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3-4" style="v" pubnumber="3,4" sid="MRK 15:3-4"/> Nsayi a pirist tukwoda a kpewo aɓo na katayi mwa. Bilatus wa nyawo ge, “Knihi zhin to hoi ɓa dna ɓe-gbe ma? Aɓeye na datu ho tukwo nyi ma?”<verse eid="MRK 15:3-4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 15:5"/>Ama Yesu to ɓei shan ɓe gbe dnam. Ca wo Bilatus n mwa.<verse eid="MRK 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 15:6"/>Kwo ɓei zhin Bilatus kunnu nu n Paska esa, wa loʼza wan-wan ya ga a Yahudawayi, ezaho-zaho yi nɓa ye. <verse eid="MRK 15:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 15:7"/>Kurkuku da ho ai yi ge Barabas. Wo ɓei zhin evi yakwo nu n na zajeyi.<verse eid="MRK 15:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 15:8"/>Safewyi, aza ya yezhi n Bilatus aba, Ɓai gyiwo wye ge wo lo eza papayi ya gaɓa gmanyi she wo shin zhin.<verse eid="MRK 15:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 15:9"/>Bilatus wa nyaɓa, “Fye ye malo a Yahudawayi osu nu ya ga fye? Owo nu n fye ye ma leya?” <verse eid="MRK 15:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 15:10"/>(Ntuge, wo ɓo ku kpe n ge a pirist tukwoda munafici nu ɓa pa, ntuge Yesu ɓei n zafun yi n duɓa.)<verse eid="MRK 15:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 15:11"/>Ama a pirist tukwoda ɓa gna aza nge ɓa gnage ɓa ye Barabas nu to ge Yesu m.<verse eid="MRK 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 15:12"/>Bilatus wa nyaɓa, “Nma lo Barabas ya, ma zhin wuna n zadeye yiʼa n fye yi ge efye ʼsu nyia?”<verse eid="MRK 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 15:13"/>Ɓa ye na kuyi viyan, “A zunwo du.”<verse eid="MRK 15:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 15:14"/>Bilatus wa nya ɓa, “Ntu Kniɓeya? Wo ku kniɓei nukwoyi zhan?” Ama ɓa gna aku fyi-fyi ge, “A zun wo du.”<verse eid="MRK 15:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 15:15"/>Shikwonyi Bilatus, wo aza yezhi dna, wo ye njesun aza yewo wa lo Barabas ya. Wa ga gbe ge a zhin Yesu bulala n bulalayi n kwo na sinknayi fyi. Wa gawo m ɓa kun nge ɓa zun wo du.<verse eid="MRK 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16-17" style="v" pubnumber="16,17" sid="MRK 15:16-17"/> A Romayi a soja ɓa la wo lo cei n bariki, ɓa yi a soja je ɓe cei, ɓa kpewo aje asu nya pya, ɓa zhin lawonyi aknawuyi nya, ɓa kun wo n tukwo. <verse eid="MRK 15:16-17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 15:18"/>Ɓa ya zhi ɓai sa wo ami, ɓai ci ge, Shekwomwasa, osu a Yahudiyi nya. <verse eid="MRK 15:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 15:19"/>Ɓaluwo n tukwo n na busiyi ɓa kni akni kpewo, ɓa kni a kwo-kwo zhi ɓai ɓiwo gna agyekpe nya.<verse eid="MRK 15:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 15:20"/>Sanu n na ɓei kuɓa ɓe mɓa wyefan agye-kpe nya yi, ɓa kma woje mɓa ɓei kpewo nyi ɓa kpe Wo owohin aje njesun ɓa lo woi a zunwo du.<verse eid="MRK 15:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 15:21"/>Siman Siriniyi, woye bwa loloɓe, ayi wo wa ɓe wa bma Yesu zundu la (Siman nu zhin Alezanda dada n Rufus yi.)<verse eid="MRK 15:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 15:22"/>Ɓaɓe n Yesu yi aba n na yi ge Golgota (wato Kwalluwa nu). <verse eid="MRK 15:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 15:23"/>Agawo nuwan mamayi to wa yesin ɓom. <verse eid="MRK 15:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 15:24"/>Ɓa pmi ɓa zunwo-du ɓa she kuriya n wa je tukwo.<verse eid="MRK 15:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 15:25"/>Ɓa ɓei zunwo du n sinkna ciwagmanyi nu n labmi yi.<verse eid="MRK 15:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 15:26"/>Ɓa ka nya kpe n wo Zundu she, ɓai wuwo laifi, “A Yahudawayi ʼsu.”<verse eid="MRK 15:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 15:27"/>Aɓei zun wodu n gnisun na vihoyi nu gun-aba n labmi yi, gmanyi nwo bwapmi, gmanyi nwo bwai-zhe bwa. <verse eid="MRK 15:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 15:28"/>Anabi ɓeda nwo ɓei da ge, “Aɓa Wo ɓedo na laifi da yi,” nyi kwa ku nu.<verse eid="MRK 15:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29-30" style="v" pubnumber="29,30" sid="MRK 15:29-30"/> A zokwo wanhi ɓai duya ɓai bmiya ba tukwo, ɓai da ɓeda nukwoyi agyekpe nya, ɓai gna, “Gye oza nwo gna ge wo ɓa mi wa ɓa aduwa nyakun ya, waje ɓa mi dna anyipyei ngun ata. Gni hohin ha ka shi nzundu.”<verse eid="MRK 15:29-30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 15:31"/>A pirist tukwoda n na adini amalemi yi bei zhi ɓo ɓai kpe Yesu agye. Bai cige, “Wo mi n na zaje gni ɓo, ama wo tami wa gni wo hin m.”<verse eid="MRK 15:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 15:32"/>Ba yaku kpewo, “Wo tunu. A Israila yi Esu, kashi n zundu n na bai ya gaho gaiciya.” Harma aviyi ngun aba ɓai kniwa kmi.<verse eid="MRK 15:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 15:33"/>Nyipyeyi atukwogunyi ekni vinya kwa dna wyegma har sinkna ngun ata wyeshe nya, wyegma yi yedna. <verse eid="MRK 15:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 15:34"/>Yesu wa yi n begye Kalayi, “Eli, Eli Lama Sabach thani” (Emi Shekwoyi, emi Shekwoyi, kni nu zhin hoi yamiʼa?)<verse eid="MRK 15:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 15:35"/>Aza m ɓa ɓei ihi ɓo, ɓa gye ge wo yi Annabi Iliya nu. <verse eid="MRK 15:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 15:36"/>Ntu cenu zaknayi wa busi ɓe n nuwan mamayi shi n fi n soso wa kuwo ko ngbe n busiyi. Fye pmi ya gye, kwo Iliya ɓa ɓe wa kawo shi.<verse eid="MRK 15:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 15:37"/>Safyewyi Yesu wa je wyisa n kalayi wa gna wo zafun a mi.<verse eid="MRK 15:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 15:38"/>Labule nkwo ɓei sa n na aduwa nyakun nyi kwa saya n she har ekni.<verse eid="MRK 15:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 15:39"/>Sanu Romawayi soja Tukwoda ɓei gye shi wo ɓei gnawo zafun ami, wa cige, “ɓehin-hin, wo ɓei zhin Shekwoyi Nugun nu.”<verse eid="MRK 15:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 15:40"/>Anyi-kwoza ho ɓai shi awye n tagni-Maryamu Magadalin, Maryamu (Yakubu Biyi n Joses ya yi), Salomi, n naza-je yi. <verse eid="MRK 15:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 15:41"/>Oɓa n na Galiliyi anyikwo aje yi mɓa zhin owo aviyi nyi, ɓa bma wozhin n na tun-tnuyi sa nwo ɓei dna n Galili nyi, ɓa ɓe Urushelima ngnisun nwoi.<verse eid="MRK 15:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42-43" style="v" pubnumber="42,43" sid="MRK 15:42-43"/> Aɓeye vinya ɓei zhin n Jumawyi nu. Dna n wyeshe yi mi Yusufu Arimatiya ʼza yakwo dna na Yahudawayi apadawa (nwo-hin tukwo wo ɓei pmi Shekwoyi bemi ɓeɓe). Wa bwa bugba kala wa lo Bilatus aba wa nyawo Yesu nayi ɓo i wa bi.<verse eid="MRK 15:42-43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 15:44"/>To Bilatus wa ga gaiciya ge Yesu la fin Ntu lonu wayi Romawayi soja gadi tukwoda wa In Yawo. <verse eid="MRK 15:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 15:45"/>Soja tukwodayi wa gna Bilatus ge, wola fi. Bilatus wa ga Yusufu gbe wa la Yesu nayi.<verse eid="MRK 15:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 15:46"/>Yusufu wa si linen ʼje, wa ka Yesu shi n zundu, wa puwo linin ʼje yi, wa yawo dna n vingwo n wo ɓei jikwo nna pma, wa pmi kutaya lo cei wa gu kwo n vingwo gbe.<verse eid="MRK 15:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 15:47"/>Maryamu Magadalin n Maryamu Yesu ʼya yi ɓei zhi ɓai shi awye she a bi Yesu.<verse eid="MRK 15:47"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="MRK 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Wo La Lakala</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 16:1"/>Sanu n Satiwyi ɓei la duya Maryamu Magadalin n Salomi yi, n Maryamu Yakubu ʼya yi ɓa kun yalo n emi sinda-yi nya yi shi n na shin zafi to wa bwo nyin <verse eid="MRK 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 16:2"/>Nla-bmiyi, nyipyei kpeɓe, ɓa lo Yesu vingwo n emiyi hoi shi. <verse eid="MRK 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 16:3"/>Ɓalo ɓai da n zokwo shi ɓa ɓe kpe vingwo kutaya n kwo gu n vingwo bwo nyi.<verse eid="MRK 16:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 16:4"/>Ama shi ɓa ɓei si ɓa gye kuta-shanwoyi n pmiya shi, n vingwoyi guya gni. <verse eid="MRK 16:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 16:5"/>Ɓalo vingwo mi ɓa gye ɓiniyi sase tu n bwai-zhe-bwa n na aje bui kpe. Ceʼa wo anyikwo-zayi. <verse eid="MRK 16:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 16:6"/>Ama Malaika cige, “Ceto wo fyem. Fye ta zan Yesu Nazaratiyi nu shin, n na ɓei zun wo du nyin? Wo to dna lo yam. Wo la laka n vingwo. Fye gye aba nu nwo nayi ɓei shi. <verse eid="MRK 16:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 16:7"/>Fye lo n sayiye fye gna Owabara nabari deye (n Bitrus yi ɓe). Yesu gyilo n fya-bye woi lo Galili fye ɓo gye wo ɓo shi wo ɓei gna fye tunyi to woi fim.”<verse eid="MRK 16:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 16:8"/>Anyi-kwoza yi ɓa kun n vingwo n vinvinyi, ednayi wo ɓa ɓodo n ɓowo-woyi har to ɓa mi m ɓa daɓom.<verse eid="MRK 16:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 16:9"/>N Ladiwyi yi nu n labmiyi n Yesu ɓei laka n vingwo, eza n wo ɓei kmiwo gye Maryamu Magadalin nu – nyikwozayi n wo ɓei kun alijenu ya ngnu tnaba n wo nyi. <verse eid="MRK 16:9"/><verse number="10-11" style="v" pubnumber="10,11" sid="MRK 16:10-11"/> Wa gye abara fi n bugbawun ɓai cibwi, wa gna ɓa ge wo la gye Yesu, woi n wye-wyei lo. Ama to ɓa gawo gaiciyam. <verse eid="MRK 16:10-11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 16:12"/>N sadohoyi, dna nyipyei yimi, wa wu wohin n aza ngun aba aba ɓai kun Urushelima ɓai lo ezhi ɓiyi ho, ama to ɓa kpe woyem, ntuge wo ɓei la wohin pmibma wuɓa. <verse eid="MRK 16:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 16:13"/>Sanu mɓa ɓei kpewo ye, ɓa busi lo Urushelima ɓa wu oɓa zaje lafiya, ama to a ga ɓa gaiciyam.<verse eid="MRK 16:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 16:14"/>Nnavun, wa wu wohin n wo abara a wocei-gmanyi aba ɓai yezhi ɓai gyi nyagyi. Wa gnakni ɓa ntu ɓa tna gaiciya gaɓo. Nya kwo ɓei zhin to ɓa ga aza gaiciya mɓa ɓei gna ɓa ge ɓa ku gye wo wye nyin.<verse eid="MRK 16:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 16:15"/>Wa pmi wa gna ge, “Fye lo anyi vinya, fya zhin nabari manayi waʼazi n zaho-zahoi aba n nabaho-bahoyi yi. <verse eid="MRK 16:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 16:16"/>Aza mɓa ga gaiciya a zhinɓa baptisma, ɓa ɓa pwo. Ama aza mɓa to ga gaiciyan, a ɓei zunɓa kni.<verse eid="MRK 16:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 16:17"/>“Aza mɓa ga gaiciya ɓa ɓei zhin ampani n mi ikoyi ɓa kun aljanu ya, ɓai daɓo n na nyitala woyi yi. <verse eid="MRK 16:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 16:18"/>Ba ɓei mi ɓai wan awa to ɓaye zhinɓa nyahon, ko ɓa sin emwi, kwo ta zhin ɓa nyahon, ɓa ɓei mi ba kpe a bwa n na nyasanyi ɓa kaɓa gna.”<verse eid="MRK 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 16:19"/>Sanu Dagayi Yesu ɓei ku ɓeda zoda mɓai, a lawo lo cei n eshemi wa sase tu n Shekwoyi bwai-zhe bwa. <verse eid="MRK 16:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 16:20"/>Owo abara laɓa n bwaho-bwahoyi ɓai zhin waʼazi, Dagayi kunsun n ɓai. Wa wu ge ɓo ɓa danyi gaiciya nu, n na ɓo, awo-woyi yi mɓa bei zhin nyi.<verse eid="MRK 16:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 16"/>
</usx>
